51, "no_speech_prob": 7.448931228781763e-12}, {"id": 15, "seek": 7732, "start": 77.32, "end": 82.94, "text": " Olha, o resultado pr\u00e1tico para quem entra por aquelas portas na manh\u00e3 seguinte", "tokens": [50365, 19450, 11, 277, 28047, 582, 28234, 1690, 13026, 22284, 1515, 2373, 32098, 2436, 296, 1667, 587, 36320, 32433, 50646], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1298139061726315, "compression_ratio": 1.3636363636363635, "no_speech_prob": 8.983759049174811e-12}, {"id": 16, "seek": 7732, "start": 82.94, "end": 89.89999999999999, "text": " procurando um conhecimento espec\u00edfico \u00e9 exatamente o mesmo do inc\u00eandio.", "tokens": [50646, 9510, 374, 1806, 1105, 15440, 28317, 32741, 78, 1136, 35937, 277, 9082, 360, 834, 1307, 273, 1004, 13, 50994], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1298139061726315, "compression_ratio": 1.3636363636363635, "no_speech_prob": 8.983759049174811e-12}, {"id": 17, "seek": 7732, "start": 90.24, "end": 91.38, "text": " Sim, o efeito \u00e9 igual.", "tokens": [51011, 3998, 11, 277, 308, 35417, 1136, 10953, 13, 51068], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1298139061726315, "compression_ratio": 1.3636363636363635, "no_speech_prob": 8.983759049174811e-12}, {"id": 18, "seek": 7732, "start": 91.55999999999999, "end": 97.47999999999999, "text": " A cole\u00e7\u00e3o foi perfeitamente preservada na sua totalidade material, claro.", "tokens": [51077, 316, 45139, 2917, 6901, 680, 37434, 3439, 45905, 1538, 1667, 8233, 3217, 6014, 2527, 11, 16742, 13, 51373], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1298139061726315, "compression_ratio": 1.3636363636363635, "no_speech_prob": 8.983759049174811e-12}, {"id": 19, "seek": 9748, "start": 97.48, "end": 104.5, "text": " Mas as condi\u00e7\u00f5es estruturais que tornavam essa cole\u00e7\u00e3o minimamente \u00fatil foram destru\u00eddas.", "tokens": [50365, 5224, 382, 2224, 38038, 45899, 374, 1527, 631, 3930, 629, 85, 335, 7208, 45139, 2917, 4464, 3439, 49191, 23102, 34235, 24455, 296, 13, 50716], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1117137416025226, "compression_ratio": 1.4065420560747663, "no_speech_prob": 8.60596316432094e-12}, {"id": 20, "seek": 9748, "start": 104.92, "end": 108.06, "text": " A informa\u00e7\u00e3o t\u00e1 l\u00e1, mas \u00e9 in\u00fatil.", "tokens": [50737, 316, 48403, 7737, 7453, 11, 2300, 1136, 294, 2481, 20007, 13, 50894], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1117137416025226, "compression_ratio": 1.4065420560747663, "no_speech_prob": 8.60596316432094e-12}, {"id": 21, "seek": 9748, "start": 108.26, "end": 110.02000000000001, "text": " \u00c9 uma imagem assustadora, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [50904, 4922, 2772, 43824, 1256, 381, 23020, 11, 7024, 30, 50992], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1117137416025226, "compression_ratio": 1.4065420560747663, "no_speech_prob": 8.60596316432094e-12}, {"id": 22, "seek": 9748, "start": 110.2, "end": 116.38000000000001, "text": " E o mais louco de tudo isso \u00e9 que essa biblioteca sem cat\u00e1logo n\u00e3o \u00e9 um exerc\u00edcio imagin\u00e1rio de fic\u00e7\u00e3o.", "tokens": [51001, 462, 277, 2420, 15185, 1291, 368, 9379, 4616, 1136, 631, 7208, 34344, 1370, 496, 4361, 3857, 842, 38212, 2431, 1136, 1105, 4057, 26162, 23427, 12657, 368, 14591, 2917, 13, 51310], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1117137416025226, "compression_ratio": 1.4065420560747663, "no_speech_prob": 8.60596316432094e-12}, {"id": 23, "seek": 9748, "start": 117.26, "end": 118.26, "text": " Definitivamente n\u00e3o.", "tokens": [51354, 46245, 270, 23957, 2431, 13, 51404], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1117137416025226, "compression_ratio": 1.4065420560747663, "no_speech_prob": 8.60596316432094e-12}, {"id": 24, "seek": 11826, "start": 118.26, "end": 123.62, "text": " \u00c9 exatamente o que t\u00e1 acontecendo com o nosso mundo digital neste exato segundo.", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 35937, 277, 631, 7737, 47623, 395, 277, 14347, 7968, 4562, 34739, 454, 2513, 17954, 13, 50633], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 25, "seek": 11826, "start": 123.94, "end": 128.32, "text": " E \u00e9 por isso que a nossa investiga\u00e7\u00e3o de hoje vai fundo num conceito fascinante.", "tokens": [50649, 462, 1136, 1515, 4616, 631, 257, 15821, 4557, 6670, 368, 13458, 4405, 40201, 1031, 10413, 3528, 7184, 259, 2879, 13, 50868], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 26, "seek": 11826, "start": 128.72, "end": 133.96, "text": " Sim, n\u00f3s estamos analisando um artigo de abril de 2026.", "tokens": [50888, 3998, 11, 9738, 10382, 2624, 271, 1806, 1105, 1523, 7483, 368, 410, 24216, 368, 945, 10880, 13, 51150], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 27, "seek": 11826, "start": 134.44, "end": 134.76, "text": " Isso.", "tokens": [51174, 14887, 13, 51190], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 28, "seek": 11826, "start": 135.0, "end": 138.4, "text": " Um ensaio escrito pelo pesquisador independente Flyxion.", "tokens": [51202, 3301, 3489, 64, 1004, 49451, 12167, 9262, 15398, 5409, 4819, 1576, 29208, 313, 13, 51372], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 29, "seek": 11826, "start": 138.94, "end": 142.9, "text": " O t\u00edtulo \u00e9 De Preserva\u00e7\u00e3o para Alcan\u00e7abilidade.", "tokens": [51399, 422, 43399, 1136, 1346, 2718, 1978, 6670, 1690, 967, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 13, 51597], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 30, "seek": 11826, "start": 143.16, "end": 146.78, "text": " Em ingl\u00eas, From Preservation to Reachability.", "tokens": [51610, 3968, 35511, 11987, 11, 3358, 2718, 6864, 281, 35904, 2310, 13, 51791], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13009577664462002, "compression_ratio": 1.4296296296296296, "no_speech_prob": 9.303598690058035e-12}, {"id": 31, "seek": 14678, "start": 146.78, "end": 157.46, "text": " E a miss\u00e3o dessa nossa imers\u00e3o de hoje \u00e9 entender a diferen\u00e7a crucial entre simplesmente salvar uma informa\u00e7\u00e3o", "tokens": [50365, 462, 257, 1713, 1076, 18554, 15821, 566, 433, 1076, 368, 13458, 1136, 20054, 257, 38336, 11462, 3962, 44482, 48873, 2772, 48403, 50899], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1351436281961108, "compression_ratio": 1.4219653179190752, "no_speech_prob": 9.086289012860682e-12}, {"id": 32, "seek": 14678, "start": 157.46, "end": 162.76, "text": " e garantir que exista de fato um caminho at\u00e9 ela.", "tokens": [50899, 308, 22251, 347, 631, 2514, 64, 368, 33351, 1105, 37215, 8784, 7175, 13, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1351436281961108, "compression_ratio": 1.4219653179190752, "no_speech_prob": 9.086289012860682e-12}, {"id": 33, "seek": 14678, "start": 163.04, "end": 163.66, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [51178, 2111, 2513, 13, 51209], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1351436281961108, "compression_ratio": 1.4219653179190752, "no_speech_prob": 9.086289012860682e-12}, {"id": 34, "seek": 14678, "start": 163.96, "end": 168.8, "text": " Porque n\u00f3s como sociedade ficamos meio que obcecados em salvar coisas.", "tokens": [51224, 11287, 9738, 2617, 45789, 14591, 2151, 17706, 631, 1111, 384, 66, 4181, 846, 48873, 14567, 13, 51466], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1351436281961108, "compression_ratio": 1.4219653179190752, "no_speech_prob": 9.086289012860682e-12}, {"id": 35, "seek": 16880, "start": 168.8, "end": 176.84, "text": " A gente salva tudo, mas esquecemos completamente de construir caminhos at\u00e9 essas coisas.", "tokens": [50365, 316, 3788, 1845, 2757, 9379, 11, 2300, 28147, 38173, 28381, 368, 38445, 1945, 29140, 8784, 19277, 14567, 13, 50767], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08880319474618646, "compression_ratio": 1.478494623655914, "no_speech_prob": 1.2718271748257681e-11}, {"id": 36, "seek": 16880, "start": 177.44, "end": 183.26000000000002, "text": " E essa distin\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 o que explica o colapso silencioso que a gente t\u00e1 vivendo.", "tokens": [50797, 462, 7208, 1483, 259, 2917, 1136, 277, 631, 1490, 2262, 277, 1173, 569, 539, 3425, 30322, 9869, 631, 257, 3788, 7737, 11005, 3999, 13, 51088], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08880319474618646, "compression_ratio": 1.478494623655914, "no_speech_prob": 1.2718271748257681e-11}, {"id": 37, "seek": 16880, "start": 183.86, "end": 193.06, "text": " O problema hoje n\u00e3o \u00e9 a perda de dados, mas a perda vertiginosa das estradas que nos levam at\u00e9 eles.", "tokens": [51118, 422, 12395, 13458, 2431, 1136, 257, 680, 2675, 368, 39915, 11, 2300, 257, 680, 2675, 6509, 328, 259, 6447, 1482, 871, 48906, 631, 3269, 20445, 335, 8784, 10244, 13, 51578], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08880319474618646, "compression_ratio": 1.478494623655914, "no_speech_prob": 1.2718271748257681e-11}, {"id": 38, "seek": 19306, "start": 193.06, "end": 200.24, "text": " N\u00f3s mantemos os destinos, mas estamos literalmente dinamitando as pontes.", "tokens": [50365, 27626, 10845, 4485, 3003, 2677, 15220, 11, 2300, 10382, 20411, 4082, 3791, 335, 270, 1806, 382, 18770, 279, 13, 50724], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09418133607844717, "compression_ratio": 1.382608695652174, "no_speech_prob": 1.1995796717068075e-11}, {"id": 39, "seek": 19306, "start": 200.3, "end": 202.18, "text": " \u00c9 uma \u00f3tima forma de colocar.", "tokens": [50727, 4922, 2772, 44490, 4775, 8366, 368, 17568, 13, 50821], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09418133607844717, "compression_ratio": 1.382608695652174, "no_speech_prob": 1.1995796717068075e-11}, {"id": 40, "seek": 19306, "start": 202.7, "end": 209.28, "text": " A infraestrutura global hoje foca quase 100% da energia na preserva\u00e7\u00e3o.", "tokens": [50847, 316, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 4338, 13458, 726, 496, 28875, 2319, 4, 1120, 29469, 1667, 45905, 6670, 13, 51176], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09418133607844717, "compression_ratio": 1.382608695652174, "no_speech_prob": 1.1995796717068075e-11}, {"id": 41, "seek": 19306, "start": 209.9, "end": 216.86, "text": " A gente tem galp\u00f5es imensos, cheios de servidores, backups redundantes na nuvem.", "tokens": [51207, 316, 3788, 1383, 7660, 79, 6036, 566, 694, 329, 11, 947, 2717, 368, 1658, 38835, 11, 50160, 27830, 9327, 1667, 3822, 31651, 13, 51555], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09418133607844717, "compression_ratio": 1.382608695652174, "no_speech_prob": 1.1995796717068075e-11}, {"id": 42, "seek": 19306, "start": 217.08, "end": 220.64000000000001, "text": " Capacidade de armazenamento que beiram o infinito, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51566, 8363, 326, 6014, 368, 3726, 921, 268, 8824, 631, 312, 40359, 277, 7193, 3528, 11, 7024, 30, 51744], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09418133607844717, "compression_ratio": 1.382608695652174, "no_speech_prob": 1.1995796717068075e-11}, {"id": 43, "seek": 22064, "start": 220.64, "end": 229.55999999999997, "text": " Pois \u00e9. Os dados continuam existindo, mas o acesso a eles \u00e9 cada vez mais fr\u00e1gil.", "tokens": [50365, 48274, 1136, 13, 8875, 39915, 2993, 335, 2514, 10306, 11, 2300, 277, 49543, 257, 10244, 1136, 8411, 5715, 2420, 431, 21099, 388, 13, 50811], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12588311278301736, "compression_ratio": 1.4694835680751173, "no_speech_prob": 1.0300649222472202e-11}, {"id": 44, "seek": 22064, "start": 229.79999999999998, "end": 233.45999999999998, "text": " Ent\u00e3o, para entender a mec\u00e2nica dessa falha colossal,", "tokens": [50823, 6469, 11, 1690, 20054, 257, 25186, 9667, 2262, 18554, 3704, 1641, 48683, 304, 11, 51006], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12588311278301736, "compression_ratio": 1.4694835680751173, "no_speech_prob": 1.0300649222472202e-11}, {"id": 45, "seek": 22064, "start": 233.95999999999998, "end": 239.6, "text": " a gente precisa olhar para como a informa\u00e7\u00e3o realmente sobrevive \u00e0 passagem do tempo.", "tokens": [51031, 257, 3788, 18861, 37446, 1690, 2617, 257, 48403, 14446, 5473, 85, 488, 1531, 11497, 76, 360, 8972, 13, 51313], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12588311278301736, "compression_ratio": 1.4694835680751173, "no_speech_prob": 1.0300649222472202e-11}, {"id": 46, "seek": 22064, "start": 240.16, "end": 243.61999999999998, "text": " O autor baseia essa discuss\u00e3o na teoria dos grafos.", "tokens": [51341, 422, 19510, 3096, 654, 7208, 2248, 1076, 1667, 535, 8172, 4491, 1295, 69, 329, 13, 51514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12588311278301736, "compression_ratio": 1.4694835680751173, "no_speech_prob": 1.0300649222472202e-11}, {"id": 47, "seek": 22064, "start": 243.82, "end": 246.22, "text": " Isso mesmo. Teoria dos grafos.", "tokens": [51524, 14887, 9082, 13, 1989, 8172, 4491, 1295, 69, 329, 13, 51644], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12588311278301736, "compression_ratio": 1.4694835680751173, "no_speech_prob": 1.0300649222472202e-11}, {"id": 48, "seek": 24622, "start": 246.22, "end": 253.84, "text": " E, sendo bem sincero, quando a matem\u00e1tica entra na conversa, a coisa costuma ficar abstrata demais.", "tokens": [50365, 462, 11, 22589, 7577, 30220, 78, 11, 7770, 257, 3803, 443, 23432, 22284, 1667, 2615, 64, 11, 257, 9614, 2063, 5544, 13646, 410, 9733, 3274, 36879, 13, 50746], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 49, "seek": 24622, "start": 254.28, "end": 256.14, "text": " Certo. Vamos desempacotar isso.", "tokens": [50768, 383, 13098, 13, 10894, 730, 15970, 326, 310, 289, 4616, 13, 50861], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 50, "seek": 24622, "start": 256.48, "end": 256.88, "text": " Vamos l\u00e1.", "tokens": [50878, 10894, 7453, 13, 50898], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 51, "seek": 24622, "start": 257.06, "end": 262.28, "text": " \u00c9 verdade que sou o abstrato, mas a aplica\u00e7\u00e3o aqui \u00e9 bastante visual, sabe?", "tokens": [50907, 4922, 15203, 631, 6926, 277, 410, 9733, 2513, 11, 2300, 257, 25522, 37823, 3871, 1136, 14651, 5056, 11, 12275, 30, 51168], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 52, "seek": 24622, "start": 262.48, "end": 264.68, "text": " Pensa em qualquer sistema sem\u00e2ntico.", "tokens": [51178, 430, 23364, 846, 20437, 13245, 4361, 3201, 580, 2789, 13, 51288], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 53, "seek": 24622, "start": 265.08, "end": 266.02, "text": " T\u00e1. Tipo a internet.", "tokens": [51308, 20907, 13, 18210, 78, 257, 4705, 13, 51355], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667774117511252, "compression_ratio": 1.3940886699507389, "no_speech_prob": 9.018955721140642e-12}, {"id": 54, "seek": 26602, "start": 266.02, "end": 273.56, "text": " Isso. A internet, ou uma biblioteca f\u00edsica, ou at\u00e9 mesmo boca a boca de uma pequena vila.", "tokens": [50365, 14887, 13, 316, 4705, 11, 2820, 2772, 34344, 1370, 496, 46436, 11, 2820, 8784, 9082, 34624, 257, 34624, 368, 2772, 26758, 4118, 371, 7371, 13, 50742], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11595272231887985, "compression_ratio": 1.3777777777777778, "no_speech_prob": 9.489601812684434e-12}, {"id": 55, "seek": 26602, "start": 274.26, "end": 277.74, "text": " Todos eles s\u00e3o compostos por duas coisas fundamentais.", "tokens": [50777, 35447, 10244, 8364, 20203, 329, 1515, 19463, 14567, 6073, 1527, 13, 50951], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11595272231887985, "compression_ratio": 1.3777777777777778, "no_speech_prob": 9.489601812684434e-12}, {"id": 56, "seek": 26602, "start": 278.29999999999995, "end": 281.82, "text": " Primeiro temos os estados, que a gente pode chamar de n\u00f3s.", "tokens": [50979, 9655, 5182, 14247, 3003, 871, 4181, 11, 631, 257, 3788, 7468, 8268, 289, 368, 9738, 13, 51155], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11595272231887985, "compression_ratio": 1.3777777777777778, "no_speech_prob": 9.489601812684434e-12}, {"id": 57, "seek": 26602, "start": 281.97999999999996, "end": 284.64, "text": " Que seria a informa\u00e7\u00e3o parada, certo?", "tokens": [51163, 4493, 20809, 257, 48403, 971, 1538, 11, 22261, 30, 51296], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11595272231887985, "compression_ratio": 1.3777777777777778, "no_speech_prob": 9.489601812684434e-12}, {"id": 58, "seek": 26602, "start": 284.9, "end": 290.4, "text": " Exato. Um documento PDF, uma p\u00e1gina web, um livro na estante.", "tokens": [51309, 2111, 2513, 13, 3301, 4166, 78, 17752, 11, 2772, 36960, 3670, 11, 1105, 33545, 1667, 871, 2879, 13, 51584], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11595272231887985, "compression_ratio": 1.3777777777777778, "no_speech_prob": 9.489601812684434e-12}, {"id": 59, "seek": 29040, "start": 290.4, "end": 297.41999999999996, "text": " O segundo componente s\u00e3o as transforma\u00e7\u00f5es, que a gente visualiza como as arestas desse grafo.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 17954, 4026, 1576, 8364, 382, 4088, 17971, 11, 631, 257, 3788, 5056, 13427, 2617, 382, 366, 372, 296, 17864, 1295, 16931, 13, 50716], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 60, "seek": 29040, "start": 297.53999999999996, "end": 299.58, "text": " Ent\u00e3o, as arestas s\u00e3o os caminhos.", "tokens": [50722, 6469, 11, 382, 366, 372, 296, 8364, 3003, 1945, 29140, 13, 50824], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 61, "seek": 29040, "start": 299.97999999999996, "end": 303.02, "text": " Aham. Os caminhos din\u00e2micos de navega\u00e7\u00e3o.", "tokens": [50844, 2438, 335, 13, 8875, 1945, 29140, 3791, 24484, 9940, 368, 39376, 3680, 2917, 13, 50996], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 62, "seek": 29040, "start": 303.46, "end": 305.73999999999995, "text": " \u00c9 o hiperlink que a gente clica.", "tokens": [51018, 4922, 277, 4879, 610, 22473, 631, 257, 3788, 596, 2262, 13, 51132], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 63, "seek": 29040, "start": 306.21999999999997, "end": 311.47999999999996, "text": " \u00c9 uma busca num cat\u00e1logo, ou uma cita\u00e7\u00e3o no rodap\u00e9 de uma p\u00e1gina de um livro.", "tokens": [51156, 4922, 2772, 37492, 1031, 3857, 842, 38212, 11, 2820, 2772, 269, 2786, 2917, 572, 8685, 569, 526, 368, 2772, 36960, 368, 1105, 33545, 13, 51419], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 64, "seek": 29040, "start": 311.9, "end": 313.32, "text": " Hum, espera um pouco.", "tokens": [51440, 12877, 11, 37862, 1105, 13920, 13, 51511], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 65, "seek": 29040, "start": 313.9, "end": 319.46, "text": " Quando a gente fala de transforma\u00e7\u00e3o, eu imagino logo c\u00e1lculos complexos, sabe?", "tokens": [51540, 18725, 257, 3788, 21580, 368, 4088, 6670, 11, 2228, 2576, 2982, 9699, 6476, 75, 32397, 3997, 329, 11, 12275, 30, 51818], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10902792358398437, "compression_ratio": 1.576470588235294, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260763592950806e-11}, {"id": 66, "seek": 31946, "start": 319.46, "end": 324.34, "text": " Como isso funciona para quem est\u00e1 apenas, sei l\u00e1, navegando pela internet, pelo celular?", "tokens": [50365, 11913, 4616, 26210, 1690, 13026, 3192, 18561, 11, 10842, 7453, 11, 39376, 70, 1806, 14820, 4705, 11, 12167, 32378, 30, 50609], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 67, "seek": 31946, "start": 324.68, "end": 326.18, "text": " \u00c9 um excelente ponto.", "tokens": [50626, 4922, 1105, 24015, 1576, 17936, 13, 50701], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 68, "seek": 31946, "start": 326.78, "end": 329.18, "text": " Pensa no ato de clicar em um link.", "tokens": [50731, 430, 23364, 572, 412, 78, 368, 596, 7953, 846, 1105, 2113, 13, 50851], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 69, "seek": 31946, "start": 329.7, "end": 332.65999999999997, "text": " N\u00e3o \u00e9 um salto m\u00e1gico do ponto A para o ponto B.", "tokens": [50877, 8010, 1136, 1105, 1845, 1353, 12228, 70, 2789, 360, 17936, 316, 1690, 277, 17936, 363, 13, 51025], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 70, "seek": 31946, "start": 333.15999999999997, "end": 339.7, "text": " O link \u00e9 uma instru\u00e7\u00e3o ativa, uma transforma\u00e7\u00e3o literal do estado do seu navegador.", "tokens": [51050, 422, 2113, 1136, 2772, 1058, 894, 2917, 412, 5931, 11, 2772, 4088, 6670, 20411, 360, 18372, 360, 7986, 39376, 70, 5409, 13, 51377], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 71, "seek": 31946, "start": 339.82, "end": 342.26, "text": " Ele faz toda uma rota f\u00edsica, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51383, 8024, 4375, 11687, 2772, 4297, 64, 46436, 11, 7024, 30, 51505], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 72, "seek": 31946, "start": 342.58, "end": 343.21999999999997, "text": " Exatamente.", "tokens": [51521, 2111, 25354, 13, 51553], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12124948047456287, "compression_ratio": 1.4588744588744589, "no_speech_prob": 9.94527984271576e-12}, {"id": 73, "seek": 34322, "start": 343.22, "end": 359.04, "text": " O sistema pega o URL, consulta o servidor DNS, traduz isso para um endere\u00e7o IP, envia uma requisi\u00e7\u00e3o para outro servidor do outro lado do mundo e traz os pacotes de dados de volta.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 13245, 43005, 277, 12905, 11, 7189, 64, 277, 1658, 29718, 35153, 11, 2479, 3334, 4616, 1690, 1105, 917, 323, 8560, 8671, 11, 2267, 654, 2772, 1724, 8021, 2917, 1690, 13170, 1658, 29718, 360, 13170, 11631, 360, 7968, 308, 37481, 3003, 15165, 17251, 368, 39915, 368, 18765, 13, 51156], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09162752768572639, "compression_ratio": 1.327485380116959, "no_speech_prob": 8.539916170058337e-12}, {"id": 74, "seek": 34322, "start": 359.28000000000003, "end": 362.84000000000003, "text": " Caramba! \u00c9 um mecanismo log\u00edstico pesado.", "tokens": [51168, 2741, 23337, 0, 4922, 1105, 385, 7035, 6882, 3565, 19512, 2789, 9262, 1573, 13, 51346], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09162752768572639, "compression_ratio": 1.327485380116959, "no_speech_prob": 8.539916170058337e-12}, {"id": 75, "seek": 36284, "start": 362.84, "end": 364.23999999999995, "text": " Muito pesado.", "tokens": [50365, 31824, 9262, 1573, 13, 50435], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1362849662178441, "compression_ratio": 1.3410404624277457, "no_speech_prob": 1.0381810862380991e-11}, {"id": 76, "seek": 36284, "start": 364.23999999999995, "end": 368.15999999999997, "text": " \u00c9 uma travessia l\u00f3gica e f\u00edsica.", "tokens": [50435, 4922, 2772, 11783, 442, 654, 48475, 2262, 308, 46436, 13, 50631], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1362849662178441, "compression_ratio": 1.3410404624277457, "no_speech_prob": 1.0381810862380991e-11}, {"id": 77, "seek": 36284, "start": 369.02, "end": 379.46, "text": " E o que o Flyxion aponta de forma brilhante \u00e9 que a preserva\u00e7\u00e3o cuida apenas de manter o documento vivo l\u00e1 no servidor de destino.", "tokens": [50674, 462, 277, 631, 277, 29208, 313, 1882, 45442, 368, 8366, 738, 388, 71, 2879, 1136, 631, 257, 45905, 6670, 2702, 2887, 18561, 368, 48170, 277, 4166, 78, 30689, 7453, 572, 1658, 29718, 368, 2677, 2982, 13, 51196], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1362849662178441, "compression_ratio": 1.3410404624277457, "no_speech_prob": 1.0381810862380991e-11}, {"id": 78, "seek": 36284, "start": 379.82, "end": 384.2, "text": " Enquanto a alcan\u00e7abilidade \u00e9 a ponte inteira.", "tokens": [51214, 2193, 358, 5857, 257, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 1136, 257, 280, 10219, 2830, 4271, 13, 51433], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1362849662178441, "compression_ratio": 1.3410404624277457, "no_speech_prob": 1.0381810862380991e-11}, {"id": 79, "seek": 38420, "start": 384.2, "end": 395.94, "text": " Sim. A alcan\u00e7abilidade \u00e9 toda essa engenharia complexa que garante que o link funcione, que a rota do ponto A ao ponto B esteja desimpedida.", "tokens": [50365, 3998, 13, 316, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 1136, 11687, 7208, 1741, 268, 5854, 654, 3997, 64, 631, 3691, 2879, 631, 277, 2113, 1019, 66, 5328, 11, 631, 257, 4297, 64, 360, 17936, 316, 8130, 17936, 363, 4065, 2938, 730, 332, 3452, 2887, 13, 50952], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08424705725449783, "compression_ratio": 1.420814479638009, "no_speech_prob": 8.407374622876329e-12}, {"id": 80, "seek": 38420, "start": 396.42, "end": 402.76, "text": " E confundir essas duas coisas \u00e9 a causa raiz das nossas falhas de mem\u00f3ria coletiva.", "tokens": [50976, 462, 1497, 997, 347, 19277, 19463, 14567, 1136, 257, 23667, 3342, 590, 1482, 44041, 3704, 12438, 368, 1334, 15250, 1173, 302, 5931, 13, 51293], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08424705725449783, "compression_ratio": 1.420814479638009, "no_speech_prob": 8.407374622876329e-12}, {"id": 81, "seek": 38420, "start": 403.02, "end": 404.88, "text": " Sabe o que isso me lembra muito?", "tokens": [51306, 318, 4488, 277, 631, 4616, 385, 7495, 6198, 4945, 30, 51399], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08424705725449783, "compression_ratio": 1.420814479638009, "no_speech_prob": 8.407374622876329e-12}, {"id": 82, "seek": 38420, "start": 405.68, "end": 408.59999999999997, "text": " Uma condi\u00e7\u00e3o neurol\u00f3gica severa.", "tokens": [51439, 21939, 2224, 16661, 22510, 6623, 14047, 2262, 2802, 64, 13, 51585], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08424705725449783, "compression_ratio": 1.420814479638009, "no_speech_prob": 8.407374622876329e-12}, {"id": 83, "seek": 38420, "start": 408.74, "end": 409.68, "text": " Hum, como assim?", "tokens": [51592, 12877, 11, 2617, 8249, 30, 51639], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08424705725449783, "compression_ratio": 1.420814479638009, "no_speech_prob": 8.407374622876329e-12}, {"id": 84, "seek": 40968, "start": 409.68, "end": 419.44, "text": " Pensa comigo. \u00c9 como ter uma mem\u00f3ria perfeitamente intacta, armazenada fisicamente numa rede de neur\u00f4nios do nosso c\u00e9rebro.", "tokens": [50365, 430, 23364, 35696, 13, 4922, 2617, 1796, 2772, 1334, 15250, 680, 37434, 3439, 23493, 64, 11, 3726, 921, 268, 1538, 36609, 23653, 29080, 14328, 368, 12087, 17140, 2717, 360, 14347, 30560, 265, 9120, 13, 50853], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09153284485807124, "compression_ratio": 1.4642857142857142, "no_speech_prob": 7.775714967739322e-12}, {"id": 85, "seek": 40968, "start": 419.98, "end": 428.64, "text": " Mas, por algum motivo, os caminhos sin\u00e1pticos respons\u00e1veis por acessar e evocar essa mem\u00f3ria perderam a conex\u00e3o.", "tokens": [50880, 5224, 11, 1515, 15468, 35804, 11, 3003, 1945, 29140, 3343, 842, 662, 9940, 2914, 42530, 1515, 696, 442, 289, 308, 1073, 47993, 7208, 1334, 15250, 26971, 335, 257, 49509, 1076, 13, 51313], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09153284485807124, "compression_ratio": 1.4642857142857142, "no_speech_prob": 7.775714967739322e-12}, {"id": 86, "seek": 40968, "start": 428.92, "end": 430.48, "text": " Nossa! Sim!", "tokens": [51327, 36016, 0, 3998, 0, 51405], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09153284485807124, "compression_ratio": 1.4642857142857142, "no_speech_prob": 7.775714967739322e-12}, {"id": 87, "seek": 40968, "start": 430.74, "end": 435.7, "text": " A lembran\u00e7a existe l\u00e1 dentro. O c\u00e9rebro est\u00e1 fisicamente saud\u00e1vel.", "tokens": [51418, 316, 7495, 1443, 22930, 16304, 7453, 10856, 13, 422, 30560, 265, 9120, 3192, 36609, 23653, 47863, 20224, 13, 51666], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09153284485807124, "compression_ratio": 1.4642857142857142, "no_speech_prob": 7.775714967739322e-12}, {"id": 88, "seek": 43570, "start": 435.7, "end": 441.42, "text": " Mas a mente n\u00e3o consegue puxar aquilo de volta para a consci\u00eancia quando precisa.", "tokens": [50365, 5224, 257, 26577, 2431, 27179, 2362, 87, 289, 32304, 368, 18765, 1690, 257, 39271, 9322, 7770, 18861, 13, 50651], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 89, "seek": 43570, "start": 442.74, "end": 447.09999999999997, "text": " A mem\u00f3ria est\u00e1 preservada, por\u00e9m inalcan\u00e7\u00e1vel.", "tokens": [50717, 316, 1334, 15250, 3192, 45905, 1538, 11, 1515, 4011, 294, 304, 7035, 1138, 20224, 13, 50935], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 90, "seek": 43570, "start": 447.59999999999997, "end": 451.94, "text": " O que \u00e9 fascinante aqui \u00e9 a precis\u00e3o mec\u00e2nica dessa analogia.", "tokens": [50960, 422, 631, 1136, 7184, 259, 2879, 3871, 1136, 257, 7974, 1076, 25186, 9667, 2262, 18554, 16660, 654, 13, 51177], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 91, "seek": 43570, "start": 452.59999999999997, "end": 457.26, "text": " Porque, assim como as redes neurais dependem dessas sinapses para o acesso,", "tokens": [51210, 11287, 11, 8249, 2617, 382, 16762, 12087, 1527, 5672, 443, 40083, 3343, 2382, 279, 1690, 277, 49543, 11, 51443], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 92, "seek": 43570, "start": 457.86, "end": 462.91999999999996, "text": " os nossos sistemas de conhecimento dependem de infraestruturas muito distintas.", "tokens": [51473, 3003, 35378, 48720, 368, 15440, 28317, 5672, 443, 368, 23654, 377, 24316, 12907, 4945, 31489, 296, 13, 51726], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 93, "seek": 43570, "start": 462.91999999999996, "end": 465.44, "text": " S\u00e3o departamentos diferentes, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51726, 22401, 9110, 28775, 17686, 11, 7024, 30, 51852], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10158678270735831, "compression_ratio": 1.5291828793774318, "no_speech_prob": 8.606977110192648e-12}, {"id": 94, "seek": 46570, "start": 465.7, "end": 467.36, "text": " Completamente separados.", "tokens": [50365, 31804, 3439, 3128, 4181, 13, 50448], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 95, "seek": 46570, "start": 467.8, "end": 474.06, "text": " As equipes corporativas que cuidam do backup dos bancos de dados para garantir que o texto n\u00e3o suma,", "tokens": [50470, 1018, 5037, 279, 6804, 35725, 631, 20770, 335, 360, 14807, 4491, 39612, 329, 368, 39915, 1690, 22251, 347, 631, 277, 35503, 2431, 2408, 64, 11, 50783], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 96, "seek": 46570, "start": 474.53999999999996, "end": 480.3, "text": " n\u00e3o s\u00e3o as mesmas equipes que desenvolvem os algoritmos de busca ou que padronizam as URLs.", "tokens": [50807, 2431, 8364, 382, 3813, 3799, 5037, 279, 631, 28683, 31651, 3003, 3501, 50017, 3415, 368, 37492, 2820, 631, 6887, 2044, 590, 335, 382, 43267, 13, 51095], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 97, "seek": 46570, "start": 481.02, "end": 485.02, "text": " \u00c9. Como s\u00e3o m\u00e1quinas separadas, elas quebram de formas diferentes.", "tokens": [51131, 4922, 13, 11913, 8364, 39701, 17094, 3128, 6872, 11, 23003, 631, 1443, 335, 368, 33463, 17686, 13, 51331], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 98, "seek": 46570, "start": 485.52, "end": 486.2, "text": " Exatamente.", "tokens": [51356, 2111, 25354, 13, 51390], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 99, "seek": 46570, "start": 487.34, "end": 489.53999999999996, "text": " Preservar, no fim das contas, \u00e9 f\u00e1cil.", "tokens": [51447, 2718, 1978, 289, 11, 572, 31603, 1482, 660, 296, 11, 1136, 17474, 13, 51557], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 100, "seek": 46570, "start": 489.8, "end": 490.5, "text": " Basta copiar.", "tokens": [51570, 363, 12468, 2971, 9448, 13, 51605], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 101, "seek": 46570, "start": 490.88, "end": 495.21999999999997, "text": " Agora, manter o caminho aberto exige manuten\u00e7\u00e3o constante.", "tokens": [51624, 16023, 11, 48170, 277, 37215, 410, 13098, 454, 3969, 587, 7886, 2917, 47343, 13, 51841], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14399411010742189, "compression_ratio": 1.5255474452554745, "no_speech_prob": 1.0414382030365932e-11}, {"id": 102, "seek": 49522, "start": 495.22, "end": 504.38000000000005, "text": " E \u00e9 assustador perceber como essa fratura entre preservar e acessar se manifesta na pr\u00e1tica para todos n\u00f3s.", "tokens": [50365, 462, 1136, 1256, 381, 5409, 49376, 2617, 7208, 431, 19660, 3962, 45905, 289, 308, 696, 442, 289, 369, 8173, 7841, 1667, 582, 23432, 1690, 6321, 9738, 13, 50823], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07885589097675524, "compression_ratio": 1.36, "no_speech_prob": 8.707317852851837e-12}, {"id": 103, "seek": 49522, "start": 505.12, "end": 510.96000000000004, "text": " Existem padr\u00f5es muito claros de como a gente quebra essas pontes no nosso dia a dia digital.", "tokens": [50860, 2111, 43958, 6887, 81, 6036, 4945, 6093, 329, 368, 2617, 257, 3788, 631, 6198, 19277, 18770, 279, 572, 14347, 6801, 257, 6801, 4562, 13, 51152], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07885589097675524, "compression_ratio": 1.36, "no_speech_prob": 8.707317852851837e-12}, {"id": 104, "seek": 51096, "start": 510.96, "end": 513.24, "text": " O artigo detalha isso muito bem.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 1523, 7483, 33185, 1641, 4616, 4945, 7577, 13, 50479], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 105, "seek": 51096, "start": 513.24, "end": 518.92, "text": " Sim, a nossa fonte de hoje tra\u00e7a um mapa bem n\u00edtido dessas falhas de infraestrutura.", "tokens": [50479, 3998, 11, 257, 15821, 283, 10219, 368, 13458, 944, 5297, 1105, 44025, 7577, 297, 6712, 2925, 40083, 3704, 12438, 368, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 13, 50763], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 106, "seek": 51096, "start": 519.54, "end": 523.9399999999999, "text": " \u00c9 quase uma taxonomia da desconex\u00e3o.", "tokens": [50794, 4922, 28875, 2772, 3366, 12481, 654, 1120, 7471, 546, 87, 1076, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 107, "seek": 51096, "start": 524.56, "end": 526.36, "text": " S\u00e3o cinco grandes falhas.", "tokens": [51045, 22401, 21350, 16640, 3704, 12438, 13, 51135], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 108, "seek": 51096, "start": 527.12, "end": 527.4399999999999, "text": " Certo?", "tokens": [51173, 383, 13098, 30, 51189], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 109, "seek": 51096, "start": 527.78, "end": 529.84, "text": " Isso, cinco cen\u00e1rios principais.", "tokens": [51206, 14887, 11, 21350, 27900, 15644, 6959, 1527, 13, 51309], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 110, "seek": 51096, "start": 530.26, "end": 533.62, "text": " E a primeira delas \u00e9 muito comum nas redes sociais hoje em dia.", "tokens": [51330, 462, 257, 21158, 1103, 296, 1136, 4945, 44324, 5382, 16762, 45179, 13458, 846, 6801, 13, 51498], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16272747770268867, "compression_ratio": 1.4057971014492754, "no_speech_prob": 1.3328564814341082e-11}, {"id": 111, "seek": 53362, "start": 533.62, "end": 537.52, "text": " \u00c9 um fen\u00f4meno que ele chama de lavagem de identidade.", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 1105, 26830, 2851, 43232, 631, 1118, 40954, 368, 20923, 14767, 368, 2473, 6014, 13, 50560], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 112, "seek": 53362, "start": 538.12, "end": 540.68, "text": " Em ingl\u00eas, namespace laundering.", "tokens": [50590, 3968, 35511, 11987, 11, 5288, 17940, 17245, 1794, 13, 50718], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 113, "seek": 53362, "start": 540.96, "end": 542.38, "text": " Lavagem de identidade.", "tokens": [50732, 30966, 14767, 368, 2473, 6014, 13, 50803], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 114, "seek": 53362, "start": 542.5, "end": 544.02, "text": " Como isso funciona na pr\u00e1tica?", "tokens": [50809, 11913, 4616, 26210, 1667, 582, 23432, 30, 50885], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 115, "seek": 53362, "start": 544.34, "end": 549.86, "text": " Ocorre quando comunidades online acumulam uma grande audi\u00eancia em torno de um tema espec\u00edfico.", "tokens": [50901, 422, 19558, 265, 7770, 11040, 10284, 2950, 41343, 425, 335, 2772, 8883, 27435, 9322, 846, 3930, 1771, 368, 1105, 15854, 32741, 78, 13, 51177], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 116, "seek": 53362, "start": 550.34, "end": 555.38, "text": " Elas constroem um espa\u00e7o super rico em significado com um hist\u00f3rico de conversas.", "tokens": [51201, 2699, 296, 1817, 340, 443, 1105, 34270, 1687, 41529, 846, 3350, 1573, 395, 1105, 33196, 23776, 368, 2615, 296, 13, 51453], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 117, "seek": 53362, "start": 555.52, "end": 555.72, "text": " T\u00e1?", "tokens": [51460, 20907, 30, 51470], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 118, "seek": 53362, "start": 555.96, "end": 558.8, "text": " Um grupo no Facebook ou uma p\u00e1gina antiga.", "tokens": [51482, 3301, 20190, 572, 4384, 2820, 2772, 36960, 2511, 9900, 13, 51624], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17958198894153943, "compression_ratio": 1.4782608695652173, "no_speech_prob": 8.539899690185315e-12}, {"id": 119, "seek": 55880, "start": 558.8, "end": 559.76, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [50365, 2111, 2513, 13, 50413], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 120, "seek": 55880, "start": 560.66, "end": 567.4399999999999, "text": " E a\u00ed, de repente, a administra\u00e7\u00e3o muda o nome e o prop\u00f3sito do grupo, reaproveitando", "tokens": [50458, 462, 7461, 11, 368, 42884, 11, 257, 4968, 37864, 8933, 64, 277, 19003, 308, 277, 2365, 12994, 3528, 360, 20190, 11, 39178, 32467, 270, 1806, 50797], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 121, "seek": 55880, "start": 567.4399999999999, "end": 573.2199999999999, "text": " toda aquela audi\u00eancia para outra finalidade que n\u00e3o tem absolutamente nada a ver com a original.", "tokens": [50797, 11687, 25996, 27435, 9322, 1690, 12301, 2572, 6014, 631, 2431, 1383, 49285, 8096, 257, 1306, 395, 257, 3380, 13, 51086], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 122, "seek": 55880, "start": 573.76, "end": 574.28, "text": " Caramba.", "tokens": [51113, 2741, 23337, 13, 51139], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 123, "seek": 55880, "start": 574.8199999999999, "end": 579.9, "text": " \u00c9 tipo achar que a gente est\u00e1 entrando na nossa padaria favorita do bairro, aquela que", "tokens": [51166, 4922, 9746, 2800, 289, 631, 257, 3788, 3192, 948, 19845, 1667, 15821, 6887, 9831, 2294, 2786, 360, 272, 1246, 340, 11, 25996, 631, 51420], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 124, "seek": 55880, "start": 579.9, "end": 585.24, "text": " a gente frequenta h\u00e1 10 anos, e descobrir que da noite para o dia ela virou uma corretora", "tokens": [51420, 257, 3788, 4459, 8938, 16448, 1266, 13592, 11, 308, 45900, 631, 1120, 34429, 1690, 277, 6801, 7175, 4107, 263, 2772, 1181, 1505, 3252, 51687], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 125, "seek": 55880, "start": 585.24, "end": 586.3599999999999, "text": " de criptomoedas.", "tokens": [51687, 368, 12815, 662, 13395, 292, 296, 13, 51743], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 126, "seek": 55880, "start": 586.5999999999999, "end": 587.5999999999999, "text": " E ningu\u00e9m te avisou.", "tokens": [51755, 462, 30091, 535, 34588, 263, 13, 51805], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 127, "seek": 55880, "start": 587.8599999999999, "end": 588.2199999999999, "text": " Pois \u00e9.", "tokens": [51818, 48274, 1136, 13, 51836], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324953743905732, "compression_ratio": 1.5229681978798586, "no_speech_prob": 8.244740827556551e-12}, {"id": 128, "seek": 58822, "start": 588.22, "end": 594.38, "text": " E o mais bizarro \u00e9 que todo mundo l\u00e1 dentro age como se o p\u00e3o nunca tivesse existido,", "tokens": [50365, 462, 277, 2420, 7390, 289, 340, 1136, 631, 5149, 7968, 7453, 10856, 3205, 2617, 369, 277, 280, 1076, 13768, 256, 40812, 2514, 2925, 11, 50673], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 129, "seek": 58822, "start": 594.48, "end": 594.74, "text": " sabe?", "tokens": [50678, 12275, 30, 50691], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 130, "seek": 58822, "start": 595.1600000000001, "end": 601.4200000000001, "text": " A audi\u00eancia e as pessoas continuam l\u00e1, o endere\u00e7o \u00e9 o mesmo, mas o passado foi silenciosamente", "tokens": [50712, 316, 27435, 9322, 308, 382, 10021, 2993, 335, 7453, 11, 277, 917, 323, 8560, 1136, 277, 9082, 11, 2300, 277, 42490, 6901, 3425, 268, 23132, 3439, 51025], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 131, "seek": 58822, "start": 601.4200000000001, "end": 602.34, "text": " sobrescrito.", "tokens": [51025, 18253, 495, 66, 17492, 13, 51071], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 132, "seek": 58822, "start": 602.7, "end": 608.2, "text": " O n\u00f3 anterior, a informa\u00e7\u00e3o antiga, foi apagado daquela rota.", "tokens": [51089, 422, 6604, 22272, 11, 257, 48403, 2511, 9900, 11, 6901, 1882, 559, 1573, 1120, 41462, 4297, 64, 13, 51364], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 133, "seek": 58822, "start": 608.5, "end": 611.6, "text": " O caminho agora aponta para um falso destino.", "tokens": [51379, 422, 37215, 9851, 1882, 45442, 1690, 1105, 3704, 539, 2677, 2982, 13, 51534], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 134, "seek": 58822, "start": 612.3000000000001, "end": 617.9, "text": " E do ponto de vista da rede como um todo, isso destr\u00f3i a confian\u00e7a naquele caminho.", "tokens": [51569, 462, 360, 17936, 368, 22553, 1120, 14328, 2617, 1105, 5149, 11, 4616, 2677, 11721, 72, 257, 49081, 5297, 1667, 17012, 37215, 13, 51849], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09912494659423828, "compression_ratio": 1.532319391634981, "no_speech_prob": 8.506727440515949e-12}, {"id": 135, "seek": 61790, "start": 617.9, "end": 619.06, "text": " Faz todo sentido.", "tokens": [50365, 33154, 5149, 19850, 13, 50423], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2448677630037875, "compression_ratio": 1.16, "no_speech_prob": 1.0261055893856508e-11}, {"id": 136, "seek": 61790, "start": 619.06, "end": 620.52, "text": " E a segunda falha?", "tokens": [50423, 462, 257, 21978, 3704, 1641, 30, 50496], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2448677630037875, "compression_ratio": 1.16, "no_speech_prob": 1.0261055893856508e-11}, {"id": 137, "seek": 61790, "start": 620.52, "end": 627.66, "text": " A segunda falha opera numa dire\u00e7\u00e3o oposta, mas tem um resultado bem parecido.", "tokens": [50496, 316, 21978, 3704, 1641, 22202, 29080, 1264, 2917, 999, 8638, 11, 2300, 1383, 1105, 28047, 7577, 7448, 17994, 13, 50853], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2448677630037875, "compression_ratio": 1.16, "no_speech_prob": 1.0261055893856508e-11}, {"id": 138, "seek": 62766, "start": 627.66, "end": 631.8199999999999, "text": " E ela atinge sistemas gigantes de refer\u00eancia.", "tokens": [50365, 462, 7175, 412, 8735, 48720, 8741, 9327, 368, 2864, 9322, 13, 50573], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.3242557131010911, "compression_ratio": 0.9879518072289156, "no_speech_prob": 1.171807095801114e-11}, {"id": 139, "seek": 62766, "start": 631.8199999999999, "end": 635.5799999999999, "text": " \u00c9 a consolida\u00e7\u00e3o enciclop\u00e9dica.", "tokens": [50573, 4922, 257, 16054, 2887, 2917, 2058, 299, 75, 404, 7811, 2262, 13, 50761], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.3242557131010911, "compression_ratio": 0.9879518072289156, "no_speech_prob": 1.171807095801114e-11}, {"id": 140, "seek": 63558, "start": 635.58, "end": 638.86, "text": " O maior exemplo disso \u00e9 a Wikip\u00e9dia.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 15859, 16496, 20088, 1136, 257, 23377, 647, 7811, 654, 13, 50529], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 141, "seek": 63558, "start": 638.86, "end": 640.26, "text": " A Wikip\u00e9dia.", "tokens": [50529, 316, 23377, 647, 7811, 654, 13, 50599], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 142, "seek": 63558, "start": 640.26, "end": 642.9200000000001, "text": " Mas espera a\u00ed, vamos olhar isso por outro \u00e2ngulo.", "tokens": [50599, 5224, 37862, 7461, 11, 5295, 37446, 4616, 1515, 13170, 20621, 37308, 13, 50732], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 143, "seek": 63558, "start": 643.5400000000001, "end": 650.3000000000001, "text": " Consolidar informa\u00e7\u00f5es e limpar a bagun\u00e7a para entregar um texto claro n\u00e3o \u00e9 o papel", "tokens": [50763, 6923, 401, 48133, 42542, 308, 2364, 2181, 257, 3411, 409, 5297, 1690, 3962, 2976, 1105, 35503, 16742, 2431, 1136, 277, 24710, 51101], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 144, "seek": 63558, "start": 650.3000000000001, "end": 652.4000000000001, "text": " fundamental de uma enciclop\u00e9dia?", "tokens": [51101, 8088, 368, 2772, 2058, 299, 75, 404, 7811, 654, 30, 51206], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 145, "seek": 63558, "start": 652.5200000000001, "end": 653.72, "text": " A princ\u00edpio, sim.", "tokens": [51212, 316, 3024, 66, 28236, 1004, 11, 1034, 13, 51272], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18664799666986231, "compression_ratio": 1.3423913043478262, "no_speech_prob": 1.19929569747379e-11}, {"id": 146, "seek": 65372, "start": 653.72, "end": 658.9, "text": " Especialmente no n\u00edvel de ru\u00eddo absurdo em que a gente vive hoje, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [50365, 2313, 494, 1013, 4082, 572, 41747, 368, 5420, 28470, 1950, 374, 2595, 846, 631, 257, 3788, 28927, 13458, 11, 7024, 30, 50624], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 147, "seek": 65372, "start": 659.5600000000001, "end": 665.6, "text": " Por que diabos limpar o texto seria um defeito de design da nossa infraestrutura?", "tokens": [50657, 5269, 631, 33227, 329, 2364, 2181, 277, 35503, 20809, 1105, 7486, 3528, 368, 1715, 1120, 15821, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 30, 50959], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 148, "seek": 65372, "start": 665.8000000000001, "end": 667.48, "text": " \u00c9 uma \u00f3tima provoca\u00e7\u00e3o.", "tokens": [50969, 4922, 2772, 44490, 4775, 1439, 24035, 2917, 13, 51053], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 149, "seek": 65372, "start": 668.0, "end": 674.34, "text": " O ponto \u00e9 que no n\u00edvel estrutural, essa limpeza gera uma compress\u00e3o de caminhos com", "tokens": [51079, 422, 17936, 1136, 631, 572, 41747, 45899, 1807, 11, 7208, 2364, 494, 2394, 41289, 2772, 14778, 1076, 368, 1945, 29140, 395, 51396], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 150, "seek": 65372, "start": 674.34, "end": 677.0400000000001, "text": " perda de dados, com perda de contexto.", "tokens": [51396, 680, 2675, 368, 39915, 11, 395, 680, 2675, 368, 47685, 13, 51531], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 151, "seek": 65372, "start": 677.44, "end": 680.38, "text": " Hum, compress\u00e3o com perda de contexto.", "tokens": [51551, 12877, 11, 14778, 1076, 395, 680, 2675, 368, 47685, 13, 51698], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1324753221475853, "compression_ratio": 1.5746606334841629, "no_speech_prob": 1.0062433525304115e-11}, {"id": 152, "seek": 68038, "start": 680.38, "end": 687.9, "text": " Pensa bem, quando ocorrem debates longos sobre um tema pol\u00eamico e o consenso muda ao longo", "tokens": [50365, 430, 23364, 7577, 11, 7770, 10409, 284, 2579, 24203, 938, 329, 5473, 1105, 15854, 1180, 13213, 2789, 308, 277, 1014, 268, 539, 8933, 64, 8130, 40558, 50741], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09344752629597981, "compression_ratio": 1.400921658986175, "no_speech_prob": 7.959992040507124e-12}, {"id": 153, "seek": 68038, "start": 687.9, "end": 693.9399999999999, "text": " dos anos, os artigos antigos s\u00e3o mesclados ou totalmente reescritos.", "tokens": [50741, 4491, 13592, 11, 3003, 1523, 13348, 2511, 13348, 8364, 3813, 3474, 4181, 2820, 30865, 319, 279, 32255, 329, 13, 51043], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09344752629597981, "compression_ratio": 1.400921658986175, "no_speech_prob": 7.959992040507124e-12}, {"id": 154, "seek": 68038, "start": 694.58, "end": 699.32, "text": " A Wikip\u00e9dia otimiza a navegabilidade para quem quer uma resposta r\u00e1pida hoje.", "tokens": [51075, 316, 23377, 647, 7811, 654, 4337, 12526, 64, 257, 39376, 70, 5177, 6014, 1690, 13026, 7083, 2772, 42126, 18213, 2887, 13458, 13, 51312], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09344752629597981, "compression_ratio": 1.400921658986175, "no_speech_prob": 7.959992040507124e-12}, {"id": 155, "seek": 68038, "start": 699.8, "end": 700.5, "text": " \u00c9 verdade.", "tokens": [51336, 4922, 15203, 13, 51371], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09344752629597981, "compression_ratio": 1.400921658986175, "no_speech_prob": 7.959992040507124e-12}, {"id": 156, "seek": 68038, "start": 701.02, "end": 704.74, "text": " T\u00e1, o texto final fica bonitinho e f\u00e1cil de ler.", "tokens": [51397, 20907, 11, 277, 35503, 2572, 16868, 4428, 270, 7775, 308, 17474, 368, 32068, 13, 51583], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09344752629597981, "compression_ratio": 1.400921658986175, "no_speech_prob": 7.959992040507124e-12}, {"id": 157, "seek": 70474, "start": 704.74, "end": 711.08, "text": " Sim, mas ela destr\u00f3i as estradas que nos permitiriam investigar como aquele consenso", "tokens": [50365, 3998, 11, 2300, 7175, 2677, 11721, 72, 382, 871, 48906, 631, 3269, 46865, 2918, 4557, 289, 2617, 23640, 1014, 268, 539, 50682], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 158, "seek": 70474, "start": 711.08, "end": 712.0600000000001, "text": " foi formado.", "tokens": [50682, 6901, 1254, 1573, 13, 50731], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 159, "seek": 70474, "start": 712.82, "end": 719.04, "text": " Toda a hist\u00f3ria anterior, com as perspectivas minorit\u00e1rias e hesita\u00e7\u00f5es, \u00e9 empurrada", "tokens": [50769, 2465, 64, 257, 20670, 22272, 11, 395, 382, 4096, 24759, 6696, 270, 24952, 308, 10453, 2786, 8001, 11, 1136, 4012, 374, 19120, 51080], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 160, "seek": 70474, "start": 719.04, "end": 721.6, "text": " para aquela aba oculta de hist\u00f3rico de edi\u00e7\u00f5es.", "tokens": [51080, 1690, 25996, 46981, 10409, 723, 64, 368, 33196, 23776, 368, 1257, 38038, 13, 51208], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 161, "seek": 70474, "start": 722.24, "end": 723.44, "text": " Ah, entendi.", "tokens": [51240, 2438, 11, 948, 13021, 13, 51300], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 162, "seek": 70474, "start": 724.02, "end": 727.5, "text": " E as pessoas normais n\u00e3o ficam vu\u00e7ando o hist\u00f3rico de edi\u00e7\u00f5es.", "tokens": [51329, 462, 382, 10021, 2026, 1527, 2431, 14591, 335, 9732, 1138, 1806, 277, 33196, 23776, 368, 1257, 38038, 13, 51503], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1222074646310708, "compression_ratio": 1.5458937198067633, "no_speech_prob": 8.742308092724027e-12}, {"id": 163, "seek": 72750, "start": 727.5, "end": 729.24, "text": " N\u00e3o s\u00f3 as pessoas.", "tokens": [50365, 8010, 6238, 382, 10021, 13, 50452], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 164, "seek": 72750, "start": 730.0, "end": 732.7, "text": " Aqui entra o detalhe t\u00e9cnico que \u00e9 crucial.", "tokens": [50490, 23089, 22284, 277, 33185, 675, 25564, 77, 2789, 631, 1136, 11462, 13, 50625], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 165, "seek": 72750, "start": 733.5, "end": 739.5, "text": " Motores de busca externos, como o Google, n\u00e3o indexam abas de hist\u00f3rico da Wikip\u00e9dia.", "tokens": [50665, 8956, 2706, 368, 37492, 30360, 329, 11, 2617, 277, 3329, 11, 2431, 8186, 335, 410, 296, 368, 33196, 23776, 1120, 23377, 647, 7811, 654, 13, 50965], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 166, "seek": 72750, "start": 739.66, "end": 740.6, "text": " Nossa, \u00e9 verdade.", "tokens": [50973, 36016, 11, 1136, 15203, 13, 51020], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 167, "seek": 72750, "start": 740.82, "end": 744.02, "text": " Voc\u00ea nunca acha o hist\u00f3rico pesquisando no Google.", "tokens": [51031, 9781, 13768, 37338, 277, 33196, 23776, 9262, 15398, 1806, 572, 3329, 13, 51191], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 168, "seek": 72750, "start": 744.18, "end": 744.66, "text": " Pois \u00e9.", "tokens": [51199, 48274, 1136, 13, 51223], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 169, "seek": 72750, "start": 745.08, "end": 750.74, "text": " Para a internet aberta, essas vis\u00f5es anteriores simplesmente deixam de existir.", "tokens": [51244, 11107, 257, 4705, 410, 22765, 11, 19277, 1452, 6036, 364, 34345, 2706, 44482, 9963, 335, 368, 2514, 347, 13, 51527], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13755556480171754, "compression_ratio": 1.4215246636771302, "no_speech_prob": 9.233900970240239e-12}, {"id": 170, "seek": 75074, "start": 750.74, "end": 757.66, "text": " O passado fica alcan\u00e7\u00e1vel apenas para quem j\u00e1 \u00e9 especialista e sabe que precisa cavar", "tokens": [50365, 422, 42490, 16868, 419, 7035, 1138, 20224, 18561, 1690, 13026, 6242, 1136, 15342, 5236, 308, 12275, 631, 18861, 13971, 289, 50711], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 171, "seek": 75074, "start": 757.66, "end": 760.92, "text": " muito fundo nos bastidores da pr\u00f3pria plataforma.", "tokens": [50711, 4945, 40201, 3269, 8414, 38835, 1120, 39608, 46243, 13, 50874], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 172, "seek": 75074, "start": 761.44, "end": 767.0, "text": " Ent\u00e3o, essa facilidade de leitura cobra um ped\u00e1gio pesado da transpar\u00eancia do processo", "tokens": [50900, 6469, 11, 7208, 10217, 6014, 368, 476, 270, 2991, 48790, 1105, 5670, 842, 17862, 9262, 1573, 1120, 1145, 2181, 9322, 360, 27939, 51178], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 173, "seek": 75074, "start": 767.0, "end": 767.6800000000001, "text": " hist\u00f3rico.", "tokens": [51178, 33196, 23776, 13, 51212], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 174, "seek": 75074, "start": 768.36, "end": 774.54, "text": " O que me leva a pensar em ped\u00e1gio literal, porque a terceira falha descrita na nossa imers\u00e3o", "tokens": [51246, 422, 631, 385, 43410, 257, 18321, 846, 5670, 842, 17862, 20411, 11, 4021, 257, 41385, 4271, 3704, 1641, 7471, 81, 2786, 1667, 15821, 566, 433, 1076, 51555], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 175, "seek": 75074, "start": 774.54, "end": 776.22, "text": " envolve dinheiro, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51555, 2267, 37361, 23760, 11, 7024, 30, 51639], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 176, "seek": 75074, "start": 776.72, "end": 779.26, "text": " Sim, a restri\u00e7\u00e3o de acesso.", "tokens": [51664, 3998, 11, 257, 1472, 470, 2917, 368, 49543, 13, 51791], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10227512668918919, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 8.740078105695659e-12}, {"id": 177, "seek": 77926, "start": 779.26, "end": 782.98, "text": " Isso atinge em cheio a pesquisa acad\u00eamica global.", "tokens": [50365, 14887, 412, 8735, 846, 947, 1004, 257, 9262, 358, 3837, 5558, 13213, 2262, 4338, 13, 50551], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 178, "seek": 77926, "start": 783.26, "end": 783.72, "text": " Pois \u00e9.", "tokens": [50565, 48274, 1136, 13, 50588], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 179, "seek": 77926, "start": 784.3, "end": 792.28, "text": " A gente tem esses identificadores digitais fant\u00e1sticos, os famosos DOIs, que s\u00e3o tipo links permanentes", "tokens": [50617, 316, 3788, 1383, 18966, 49456, 11856, 14293, 1527, 4115, 25952, 9940, 11, 3003, 1087, 33894, 10699, 6802, 11, 631, 8364, 9746, 6123, 8105, 9240, 51016], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 180, "seek": 77926, "start": 792.28, "end": 795.24, "text": " blindados para artigos cient\u00edficos.", "tokens": [51016, 6865, 4181, 1690, 1523, 13348, 37053, 329, 13, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 181, "seek": 77926, "start": 795.86, "end": 798.88, "text": " A ponte ali foi perfeitamente constru\u00edda.", "tokens": [51195, 316, 280, 10219, 10198, 6901, 680, 37434, 3439, 12946, 39080, 13, 51346], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 182, "seek": 77926, "start": 799.28, "end": 804.22, "text": " Constru\u00edda perfeitamente, mas com um muro financeiro gigante no meio dela.", "tokens": [51366, 8574, 894, 39080, 680, 37434, 3439, 11, 2300, 395, 1105, 2992, 340, 10719, 5182, 8741, 2879, 572, 17706, 21820, 13, 51613], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1527988634611431, "compression_ratio": 1.4861111111111112, "no_speech_prob": 9.906320555530534e-12}, {"id": 183, "seek": 80422, "start": 804.22, "end": 810.7, "text": " As grandes editoras acad\u00eamicas colocam esses artigos atr\u00e1s de paywalls car\u00edssimos.", "tokens": [50365, 1018, 16640, 9839, 296, 5558, 13213, 9150, 12327, 335, 18966, 1523, 13348, 22906, 368, 1689, 16256, 82, 1032, 36375, 8372, 13, 50689], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 184, "seek": 80422, "start": 810.94, "end": 816.9200000000001, "text": " O documento existe no servidor deles, ent\u00e3o a preserva\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 um sucesso absoluto.", "tokens": [50701, 422, 4166, 78, 16304, 572, 1658, 29718, 30789, 11, 9071, 257, 45905, 6670, 1136, 1105, 459, 43611, 18757, 78, 13, 51000], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 185, "seek": 80422, "start": 817.0, "end": 821.78, "text": " H\u00e1 um institucional ou um cart\u00e3o de cr\u00e9dito para ser percorrido at\u00e9 o fim.", "tokens": [51004, 389, 842, 1105, 4348, 1311, 1966, 2820, 1105, 5467, 1076, 368, 37368, 3528, 1690, 816, 680, 19558, 81, 2925, 8784, 277, 31603, 13, 51243], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 186, "seek": 80422, "start": 822.78, "end": 828.9, "text": " Estruturalmente falando, para qualquer pessoa sem v\u00ednculo com universidades de elite, essa", "tokens": [51293, 4410, 24316, 1807, 4082, 21236, 11, 1690, 20437, 16366, 4361, 6153, 77, 25436, 395, 5950, 10284, 368, 17801, 11, 7208, 51599], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 187, "seek": 80422, "start": 828.9, "end": 830.0, "text": " ponte \u00e9 in\u00fatil.", "tokens": [51599, 280, 10219, 1136, 294, 2481, 20007, 13, 51654], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 188, "seek": 80422, "start": 830.34, "end": 832.44, "text": " Ela est\u00e1 l\u00e1, mas n\u00e3o serve para nada.", "tokens": [51671, 17637, 3192, 7453, 11, 2300, 2431, 4596, 1690, 8096, 13, 51776], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09470097914985988, "compression_ratio": 1.5037593984962405, "no_speech_prob": 9.829200821320772e-12}, {"id": 189, "seek": 83244, "start": 832.44, "end": 838.98, "text": " Agora, por pior que seja encontrar uma ponte bloqueada por um paywall, pelo menos voc\u00ea", "tokens": [50365, 16023, 11, 1515, 45974, 631, 13459, 17525, 2772, 280, 10219, 41592, 1538, 1515, 1105, 1689, 16256, 11, 12167, 8902, 2723, 50692], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 190, "seek": 83244, "start": 838.98, "end": 843.1, "text": " sabe que o destino est\u00e1 l\u00e1 do outro lado, esperando por quem tem a chave.", "tokens": [50692, 12275, 631, 277, 2677, 2982, 3192, 7453, 360, 13170, 11631, 11, 46587, 1515, 13026, 1383, 257, 417, 946, 13, 50898], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 191, "seek": 83244, "start": 843.4000000000001, "end": 847.36, "text": " O que me deixa genuinamente assustado \u00e9 a quarta falha.", "tokens": [50913, 422, 631, 385, 26208, 1049, 9445, 3439, 1256, 381, 1573, 1136, 257, 421, 19061, 3704, 1641, 13, 51111], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 192, "seek": 83244, "start": 847.5400000000001, "end": 849.8800000000001, "text": " Ah, o apodrecimento de links.", "tokens": [51120, 2438, 11, 277, 1882, 378, 13867, 10030, 368, 6123, 13, 51237], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 193, "seek": 83244, "start": 850.3800000000001, "end": 850.9000000000001, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [51262, 2111, 2513, 13, 51288], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 194, "seek": 83244, "start": 851.08, "end": 852.0600000000001, "text": " O link rot.", "tokens": [51297, 422, 2113, 4297, 13, 51346], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 195, "seek": 83244, "start": 852.44, "end": 856.3000000000001, "text": " \u00c9 quando a ponte colapsa fisicamente e cai no abismo.", "tokens": [51365, 4922, 7770, 257, 280, 10219, 1173, 2382, 64, 36609, 23653, 308, 46523, 572, 410, 6882, 13, 51558], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10988848549979073, "compression_ratio": 1.4727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 1.0502885887386793e-11}, {"id": 196, "seek": 85630, "start": 856.3, "end": 863.68, "text": " Lendo a pesquisa de base para a nossa an\u00e1lise de hoje, eu esbarrei num dado chocante de um", "tokens": [50365, 441, 3999, 257, 9262, 358, 3837, 368, 3096, 1690, 257, 15821, 44113, 908, 368, 13458, 11, 2228, 785, 5356, 10271, 1031, 29568, 417, 905, 2879, 368, 1105, 50734], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08580619297670515, "compression_ratio": 1.391304347826087, "no_speech_prob": 9.563965938652608e-12}, {"id": 197, "seek": 85630, "start": 863.68, "end": 867.16, "text": " estudo da revista PLOS ONE de 2014.", "tokens": [50734, 871, 6207, 1120, 3698, 5236, 6999, 4367, 22026, 368, 8227, 13, 50908], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08580619297670515, "compression_ratio": 1.391304347826087, "no_speech_prob": 9.563965938652608e-12}, {"id": 198, "seek": 85630, "start": 867.5799999999999, "end": 870.9, "text": " Aquele estudo sobre as refer\u00eancias bibliogr\u00e1ficas, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [50929, 316, 17012, 871, 6207, 5473, 382, 2864, 32715, 34344, 47810, 23858, 296, 11, 7024, 30, 51095], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08580619297670515, "compression_ratio": 1.391304347826087, "no_speech_prob": 9.563965938652608e-12}, {"id": 199, "seek": 85630, "start": 871.06, "end": 871.8599999999999, "text": " Esse mesmo.", "tokens": [51103, 18814, 9082, 13, 51143], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08580619297670515, "compression_ratio": 1.391304347826087, "no_speech_prob": 9.563965938652608e-12}, {"id": 200, "seek": 85630, "start": 872.4599999999999, "end": 878.5, "text": " Eles descobriram que um em cada cinco artigos acad\u00eamicos cont\u00e9m refer\u00eancias que apontam", "tokens": [51173, 31096, 45900, 335, 631, 1105, 846, 8411, 21350, 1523, 13348, 5558, 13213, 9940, 660, 4011, 2864, 32715, 631, 1882, 896, 335, 51475], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08580619297670515, "compression_ratio": 1.391304347826087, "no_speech_prob": 9.563965938652608e-12}, {"id": 201, "seek": 87850, "start": 878.5, "end": 879.56, "text": " para links mortos.", "tokens": [50365, 1690, 6123, 6599, 329, 13, 50418], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 202, "seek": 87850, "start": 881.04, "end": 889.46, "text": " 20%, 20% da base do nosso conhecimento formal resulta em uma daquelas telas de erro 404 de", "tokens": [50492, 945, 8923, 945, 4, 1120, 3096, 360, 14347, 15440, 28317, 9860, 1874, 64, 846, 2772, 1120, 20593, 296, 15284, 296, 368, 45935, 3356, 19, 368, 50913], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 203, "seek": 87850, "start": 889.46, "end": 891.06, "text": " p\u00e1gina n\u00e3o encontrada.", "tokens": [50913, 36960, 2431, 10176, 19120, 13, 50993], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 204, "seek": 87850, "start": 891.16, "end": 896.96, "text": " \u00c9 um n\u00famero que ilustra a exclus\u00e3o literal da aresta no nosso grafo de conhecimento.", "tokens": [50998, 4922, 1105, 14959, 631, 1930, 381, 424, 257, 15085, 1076, 20411, 1120, 366, 9140, 572, 14347, 1295, 16931, 368, 15440, 28317, 13, 51288], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 205, "seek": 87850, "start": 897.42, "end": 899.0, "text": " Pensem como isso acontece f\u00e1cil.", "tokens": [51311, 430, 1288, 76, 2617, 4616, 19786, 17474, 13, 51390], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 206, "seek": 87850, "start": 899.4, "end": 901.44, "text": " Um dom\u00ednio esquece de ser renovado.", "tokens": [51410, 3301, 3285, 10973, 1004, 28147, 384, 368, 816, 18845, 1573, 13, 51512], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.16314720577663847, "compression_ratio": 1.4154589371980677, "no_speech_prob": 9.090469696437786e-12}, {"id": 207, "seek": 90144, "start": 901.44, "end": 905.98, "text": " Ou um servidor antigo \u00e9 desligado no por\u00e3o de algum departamento universit\u00e1rio.", "tokens": [50365, 11710, 1105, 1658, 29718, 2511, 7483, 1136, 730, 5073, 1573, 572, 1515, 1076, 368, 15468, 9110, 8824, 5950, 270, 12657, 13, 50592], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 208, "seek": 90144, "start": 906.2800000000001, "end": 912.2, "text": " Sim, ou um site apenas reorganiza as pastas internas sem criar os redirecionamentos adequados.", "tokens": [50607, 3998, 11, 2820, 1105, 3621, 18561, 41203, 13427, 382, 1791, 296, 2154, 296, 4361, 36882, 3003, 2182, 621, 10015, 28775, 15747, 4181, 13, 50903], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 209, "seek": 90144, "start": 912.6, "end": 917.7800000000001, "text": " A informa\u00e7\u00e3o original pode at\u00e9 estar viva em algum HD externo esquecido numa gaveta.", "tokens": [50923, 316, 48403, 3380, 7468, 8784, 8755, 371, 5931, 846, 15468, 12149, 454, 391, 1771, 28147, 17994, 29080, 290, 706, 7664, 13, 51182], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 210, "seek": 90144, "start": 918.1600000000001, "end": 920.5400000000001, "text": " Mas a rota at\u00e9 l\u00e1 quebrou para sempre.", "tokens": [51201, 5224, 257, 4297, 64, 8784, 7453, 631, 1443, 263, 1690, 9553, 13, 51320], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 211, "seek": 90144, "start": 920.8000000000001, "end": 926.2600000000001, "text": " A gente est\u00e1 construindo uma pir\u00e2mide de conhecimento onde um quinto dos tijolos da base", "tokens": [51333, 316, 3788, 3192, 12946, 10306, 2772, 13528, 24484, 482, 368, 15440, 28317, 14396, 1105, 421, 17246, 4491, 256, 1718, 401, 329, 1120, 3096, 51606], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 212, "seek": 90144, "start": 926.2600000000001, "end": 927.62, "text": " simplesmente virou p\u00f3.", "tokens": [51606, 44482, 4107, 263, 28157, 13, 51674], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 213, "seek": 90144, "start": 927.96, "end": 929.0200000000001, "text": " \u00c9 desesperador.", "tokens": [51691, 4922, 730, 34698, 5409, 13, 51744], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09185286930629186, "compression_ratio": 1.5208333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 8.24498715829014e-12}, {"id": 214, "seek": 92902, "start": 929.02, "end": 934.4, "text": " E isso nos leva ao quinto e \u00faltimo padr\u00e3o de desconex\u00e3o, que acho que carrega uma", "tokens": [50365, 462, 4616, 3269, 43410, 8130, 421, 17246, 308, 21013, 6887, 36837, 368, 7471, 546, 87, 1076, 11, 631, 14253, 631, 1032, 3375, 64, 2772, 50634], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 215, "seek": 92902, "start": 934.4, "end": 936.42, "text": " ironia quase tr\u00e1gica, sabe?", "tokens": [50634, 6497, 654, 28875, 504, 21099, 2262, 11, 12275, 30, 50735], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 216, "seek": 92902, "start": 936.6999999999999, "end": 940.98, "text": " O isolamento arquiv\u00edstico \u00e9 um \u00f3timo ponto.", "tokens": [50749, 422, 7381, 8824, 40258, 592, 19512, 2789, 1136, 1105, 44490, 6934, 17936, 13, 50963], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 217, "seek": 92902, "start": 941.48, "end": 948.3199999999999, "text": " O artigo usa o exemplo do artigo digital do 11 de setembro, que \u00e9 gerido pela Biblioteca", "tokens": [50988, 422, 1523, 7483, 29909, 277, 16496, 360, 1523, 7483, 4562, 360, 2975, 368, 992, 443, 9120, 11, 631, 1136, 5713, 2925, 14820, 31520, 2081, 1370, 496, 51330], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 218, "seek": 92902, "start": 948.3199999999999, "end": 950.1999999999999, "text": " do Congresso dos Estados Unidos.", "tokens": [51330, 360, 4280, 29652, 4491, 22362, 23087, 13, 51424], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 219, "seek": 92902, "start": 950.76, "end": 954.66, "text": " Que \u00e9, assim, o supra-sumo do arquivamento.", "tokens": [51452, 4493, 1136, 11, 8249, 11, 277, 9331, 424, 12, 82, 40904, 360, 40258, 592, 8824, 13, 51647], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11478058351289241, "compression_ratio": 1.4260869565217391, "no_speech_prob": 1.0586365117859486e-11}, {"id": 220, "seek": 95466, "start": 954.66, "end": 963.54, "text": " \u00c9 um projeto com financiamento pesado, tecnologia de ponta, rigor extremo da arquivologia tradicional.", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 1105, 40679, 395, 24323, 8824, 9262, 1573, 11, 44905, 368, 18770, 64, 11, 42191, 4040, 78, 1120, 40258, 592, 24103, 47956, 13, 50809], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11176189092489389, "compression_ratio": 1.3265306122448979, "no_speech_prob": 8.640727890141253e-12}, {"id": 221, "seek": 95466, "start": 964.48, "end": 970.8399999999999, "text": " Como um projeto padr\u00e3o ouro desses pode ser o grande exemplo de falha de alcan\u00e7abilidade?", "tokens": [50856, 11913, 1105, 40679, 6887, 36837, 2820, 340, 36409, 7468, 816, 277, 8883, 16496, 368, 3704, 1641, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 30, 51174], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11176189092489389, "compression_ratio": 1.3265306122448979, "no_speech_prob": 8.640727890141253e-12}, {"id": 222, "seek": 97084, "start": 970.84, "end": 977.5600000000001, "text": " \u00c9 ir\u00f4nico, mas acontece, porque ele foi constru\u00eddo como um silo impenetr\u00e1vel, sabe?", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 3418, 17140, 2789, 11, 2300, 19786, 11, 4021, 1118, 6901, 12946, 28470, 2617, 1105, 3425, 78, 704, 268, 27965, 20224, 11, 12275, 30, 50701], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10536113077280473, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260591855326684e-11}, {"id": 223, "seek": 97084, "start": 978.3000000000001, "end": 986.76, "text": " A arquitetura de dados desses arquivos de alta seguran\u00e7a costuma usar bancos de dados muito din\u00e2micos", "tokens": [50738, 316, 40258, 16341, 2991, 368, 39915, 36409, 40258, 16501, 368, 26495, 49538, 2063, 5544, 14745, 39612, 329, 368, 39915, 4945, 3791, 24484, 9940, 51161], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10536113077280473, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260591855326684e-11}, {"id": 224, "seek": 97084, "start": 986.76, "end": 990.2800000000001, "text": " e formatos de arquivo propriet\u00e1rios.", "tokens": [51161, 308, 7877, 329, 368, 40258, 6340, 27881, 15644, 13, 51337], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10536113077280473, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260591855326684e-11}, {"id": 225, "seek": 97084, "start": 990.98, "end": 994.9000000000001, "text": " E esses formatos s\u00e3o p\u00e9ssimos para indexa\u00e7\u00e3o externa.", "tokens": [51372, 462, 18966, 7877, 329, 8364, 280, 2191, 82, 8372, 1690, 8186, 6670, 454, 391, 629, 13, 51568], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10536113077280473, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260591855326684e-11}, {"id": 226, "seek": 97084, "start": 995.32, "end": 999.02, "text": " Hum, ent\u00e3o o Google n\u00e3o consegue ler o que tem l\u00e1 dentro?", "tokens": [51589, 12877, 11, 9071, 277, 3329, 2431, 27179, 32068, 277, 631, 1383, 7453, 10856, 30, 51774], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10536113077280473, "compression_ratio": 1.5, "no_speech_prob": 1.0260591855326684e-11}, {"id": 227, "seek": 99902, "start": 999.02, "end": 1007.34, "text": " Exato. O motor de busca de uso di\u00e1rio n\u00e3o consegue engolir o conte\u00fado desse arquivo de forma eficiente.", "tokens": [50365, 2111, 2513, 13, 422, 5932, 368, 37492, 368, 22728, 1026, 12657, 2431, 27179, 1741, 401, 347, 277, 44144, 17864, 40258, 6340, 368, 8366, 308, 26863, 13, 50781], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07838374824934108, "compression_ratio": 1.5066666666666666, "no_speech_prob": 8.212909519134115e-12}, {"id": 228, "seek": 99902, "start": 1008.1999999999999, "end": 1013.84, "text": " Um cidad\u00e3o comum que digita uma pesquisa casual sobre o 11 de setembro no celular", "tokens": [50824, 3301, 269, 4580, 1076, 44324, 631, 2528, 2786, 2772, 9262, 358, 3837, 13052, 5473, 277, 2975, 368, 992, 443, 9120, 572, 32378, 51106], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07838374824934108, "compression_ratio": 1.5066666666666666, "no_speech_prob": 8.212909519134115e-12}, {"id": 229, "seek": 99902, "start": 1013.84, "end": 1017.28, "text": " n\u00e3o vai trope\u00e7ar nesses documentos preservados.", "tokens": [51106, 2431, 4405, 4495, 494, 26378, 297, 32393, 4166, 329, 45905, 4181, 13, 51278], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07838374824934108, "compression_ratio": 1.5066666666666666, "no_speech_prob": 8.212909519134115e-12}, {"id": 230, "seek": 99902, "start": 1017.28, "end": 1024.2, "text": " Ou seja, se a pessoa precisa saber que o arquivo existe antes mesmo de come\u00e7ar a procurar por ele,", "tokens": [51278, 11710, 13459, 11, 369, 257, 16366, 18861, 12489, 631, 277, 40258, 6340, 16304, 11014, 9082, 368, 24379, 257, 9510, 28586, 1515, 1118, 11, 51624], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07838374824934108, "compression_ratio": 1.5066666666666666, "no_speech_prob": 8.212909519134115e-12}, {"id": 231, "seek": 102420, "start": 1024.2, "end": 1027.44, "text": " ent\u00e3o ele n\u00e3o faz parte da rede viva de conhecimento.", "tokens": [50365, 9071, 1118, 2431, 4375, 6975, 1120, 14328, 371, 5931, 368, 15440, 28317, 13, 50527], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 232, "seek": 102420, "start": 1027.76, "end": 1029.44, "text": " Ele virou uma ilha fechada.", "tokens": [50543, 8024, 4107, 263, 2772, 1930, 1641, 579, 339, 1538, 13, 50627], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 233, "seek": 102420, "start": 1029.6200000000001, "end": 1031.6000000000001, "text": " Efeito, uma ilha fechada.", "tokens": [50636, 462, 35417, 11, 2772, 1930, 1641, 579, 339, 1538, 13, 50735], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 234, "seek": 102420, "start": 1032.02, "end": 1037.24, "text": " A preserva\u00e7\u00e3o foi um sucesso, mas a alcan\u00e7abilidade p\u00fablica \u00e9 quase zero.", "tokens": [50756, 316, 45905, 6670, 6901, 1105, 459, 43611, 11, 2300, 257, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 38905, 1136, 28875, 4018, 13, 51017], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 235, "seek": 102420, "start": 1037.38, "end": 1041.0800000000002, "text": " Bom, aqui \u00e9 que a coisa fica realmente interessante.", "tokens": [51024, 19812, 11, 3871, 1136, 631, 257, 9614, 16868, 14446, 24372, 13, 51209], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 236, "seek": 102420, "start": 1041.66, "end": 1045.7, "text": " Porque quando a gente olha para todos esses exemplos de falha,", "tokens": [51238, 11287, 7770, 257, 3788, 23550, 1690, 6321, 18966, 24112, 329, 368, 3704, 1641, 11, 51440], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 237, "seek": 102420, "start": 1045.8400000000001, "end": 1051.38, "text": " desde os links apodrecidos at\u00e9 os grandes arquivos americanos isolados,", "tokens": [51447, 10188, 3003, 6123, 1882, 378, 13867, 7895, 8784, 3003, 16640, 40258, 16501, 31229, 329, 7381, 4181, 11, 51724], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09130155718004382, "compression_ratio": 1.56198347107438, "no_speech_prob": 8.506503661187548e-12}, {"id": 238, "seek": 105138, "start": 1051.38, "end": 1055.92, "text": " a nossa primeira rea\u00e7\u00e3o, o instinto b\u00e1sico, \u00e9 pensar assim.", "tokens": [50365, 257, 15821, 21158, 319, 6670, 11, 277, 1058, 17246, 25545, 2789, 11, 1136, 18321, 8249, 13, 50592], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 239, "seek": 105138, "start": 1056.5, "end": 1061.2, "text": " Ah, precisamos de computadores melhores, de algoritmos mais complexos.", "tokens": [50621, 2438, 11, 7974, 2151, 368, 2807, 11856, 46807, 11, 368, 3501, 50017, 3415, 2420, 3997, 329, 13, 50856], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 240, "seek": 105138, "start": 1061.2600000000002, "end": 1065.4, "text": " \u00c9 o que todo mundo pensa, resolver tecnologia com mais tecnologia.", "tokens": [50859, 4922, 277, 631, 5149, 7968, 46909, 11, 34480, 44905, 395, 2420, 44905, 13, 51066], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 241, "seek": 105138, "start": 1065.66, "end": 1066.24, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [51079, 2111, 2513, 13, 51108], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 242, "seek": 105138, "start": 1066.7600000000002, "end": 1070.68, "text": " Mas a nossa fonte subverte isso de um jeito genial.", "tokens": [51134, 5224, 257, 15821, 283, 10219, 1422, 331, 975, 4616, 368, 1105, 31478, 48228, 13, 51330], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 243, "seek": 105138, "start": 1071.3000000000002, "end": 1075.8000000000002, "text": " O Flyxion foca em sistemas que quase n\u00e3o usam tecnologia digital.", "tokens": [51361, 422, 29208, 313, 726, 496, 846, 48720, 631, 28875, 2431, 505, 335, 44905, 4562, 13, 51586], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11528371727984885, "compression_ratio": 1.4774774774774775, "no_speech_prob": 8.94977408155695e-12}, {"id": 244, "seek": 107580, "start": 1075.8, "end": 1081.58, "text": " Sim, ele muda o foco bruscamente para o que chama de sistemas locais densos.", "tokens": [50365, 3998, 11, 1118, 8933, 64, 277, 726, 1291, 738, 32601, 3439, 1690, 277, 631, 40954, 368, 48720, 47965, 271, 24505, 329, 13, 50654], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 245, "seek": 107580, "start": 1081.98, "end": 1085.44, "text": " Estamos falando de comunidades religiosas tradicionais,", "tokens": [50674, 34563, 21236, 368, 11040, 10284, 4039, 2717, 296, 2479, 18899, 1527, 11, 50847], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 246, "seek": 107580, "start": 1085.96, "end": 1088.6599999999999, "text": " bairros antigos com hist\u00f3rias fortes,", "tokens": [50873, 272, 1246, 2635, 2511, 13348, 395, 33196, 35051, 5009, 279, 11, 51008], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 247, "seek": 107580, "start": 1089.22, "end": 1090.56, "text": " guildas de artes\u00e3os.", "tokens": [51036, 37435, 296, 368, 1523, 279, 46550, 13, 51103], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 248, "seek": 107580, "start": 1090.78, "end": 1092.74, "text": " Grupos que operam no anal\u00f3gico.", "tokens": [51114, 10459, 30010, 631, 2208, 335, 572, 2624, 14047, 2789, 13, 51212], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 249, "seek": 107580, "start": 1092.96, "end": 1093.74, "text": " Totalmente.", "tokens": [51223, 23170, 4082, 13, 51262], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 250, "seek": 107580, "start": 1094.28, "end": 1099.1, "text": " Eles n\u00e3o t\u00eam servidores rodando em nuvem com m\u00faltiplas zonas de redund\u00e2ncia.", "tokens": [51289, 31096, 2431, 24277, 1658, 38835, 8685, 1806, 846, 3822, 31651, 395, 275, 43447, 34442, 296, 710, 38027, 368, 27830, 25677, 13, 51530], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 251, "seek": 107580, "start": 1099.58, "end": 1105.04, "text": " Eles n\u00e3o emitem identificadores digitais permanentes para cada hist\u00f3ria que contam.", "tokens": [51554, 31096, 2431, 32084, 443, 49456, 11856, 14293, 1527, 8105, 9240, 1690, 8411, 20670, 631, 20463, 13, 51827], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12622504234313964, "compression_ratio": 1.5576923076923077, "no_speech_prob": 9.193445484056983e-12}, {"id": 252, "seek": 110504, "start": 1105.04, "end": 1108.96, "text": " A preserva\u00e7\u00e3o formal deles \u00e9 praticamente inexistente.", "tokens": [50365, 316, 45905, 6670, 9860, 30789, 1136, 45734, 294, 18217, 1576, 13, 50561], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 253, "seek": 110504, "start": 1109.1399999999999, "end": 1110.1399999999999, "text": " Quase zero.", "tokens": [50570, 2326, 651, 4018, 13, 50620], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 254, "seek": 110504, "start": 1110.6399999999999, "end": 1113.18, "text": " Mesmo assim, de forma incr\u00edvel,", "tokens": [50645, 17485, 3280, 8249, 11, 368, 8366, 42211, 13185, 11, 50772], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 255, "seek": 110504, "start": 1113.6399999999999, "end": 1116.8799999999999, "text": " esses grupos mant\u00eam uma continuidade de sentido,", "tokens": [50795, 18966, 33758, 10845, 13213, 2772, 2993, 6014, 368, 19850, 11, 50957], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 256, "seek": 110504, "start": 1117.34, "end": 1120.1399999999999, "text": " uma mem\u00f3ria sem\u00e2ntica robusta,", "tokens": [50980, 2772, 1334, 15250, 4361, 3201, 580, 2262, 13956, 64, 11, 51120], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 257, "seek": 110504, "start": 1120.24, "end": 1122.92, "text": " atrav\u00e9s de d\u00e9cadas, \u00e0s vezes s\u00e9culos.", "tokens": [51125, 39941, 368, 9198, 6872, 11, 23763, 12925, 7910, 32397, 13, 51259], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 258, "seek": 110504, "start": 1123.5, "end": 1129.24, "text": " E o segredo deles \u00e9 exatamente o que revela a grande falha da internet moderna.", "tokens": [51288, 462, 277, 3896, 986, 78, 30789, 1136, 35937, 277, 631, 15262, 64, 257, 8883, 3704, 1641, 1120, 4705, 10494, 629, 13, 51575], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12859162131508628, "compression_ratio": 1.4063926940639269, "no_speech_prob": 8.506707491195975e-12}, {"id": 259, "seek": 112924, "start": 1129.24, "end": 1135.16, "text": " Para quem est\u00e1 ouvindo, d\u00e1 para visualizar isso atrav\u00e9s da imagem de uma floresta.", "tokens": [50365, 11107, 13026, 3192, 21157, 10306, 11, 14401, 1690, 5056, 9736, 4616, 39941, 1120, 43824, 368, 2772, 932, 418, 9140, 13, 50661], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 260, "seek": 112924, "start": 1135.66, "end": 1138.88, "text": " Toda essa nossa infraestrutura digital de ponta,", "tokens": [50686, 2465, 64, 7208, 15821, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 4562, 368, 18770, 64, 11, 50847], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 261, "seek": 112924, "start": 1139.68, "end": 1141.78, "text": " com os grandes buscadores globais,", "tokens": [50887, 395, 3003, 16640, 1255, 66, 11856, 16125, 1527, 11, 50992], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 262, "seek": 112924, "start": 1142.42, "end": 1148.64, "text": " opera como uma \u00fanica rodovia asfaltada, gigantesca e perfeita, cortando a selva.", "tokens": [51024, 22202, 2617, 2772, 30104, 744, 2595, 11617, 382, 69, 3198, 1538, 11, 8741, 9327, 496, 308, 680, 2106, 2786, 11, 11278, 1806, 257, 5851, 2757, 13, 51335], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 263, "seek": 112924, "start": 1148.78, "end": 1152.14, "text": " \u00c9 uma rodovia incrivelmente r\u00e1pida.", "tokens": [51342, 4922, 2772, 744, 2595, 11617, 834, 470, 39786, 18213, 2887, 13, 51510], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 264, "seek": 112924, "start": 1152.34, "end": 1153.14, "text": " Muito r\u00e1pida.", "tokens": [51520, 31824, 18213, 2887, 13, 51560], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13675476349506183, "compression_ratio": 1.4615384615384615, "no_speech_prob": 9.488619959197031e-12}, {"id": 265, "seek": 115314, "start": 1153.14, "end": 1158.74, "text": " Mas, pensa bem, se uma \u00e1rvore gigante cai no meio dessa estrada,", "tokens": [50365, 5224, 11, 46909, 7577, 11, 369, 2772, 35349, 85, 418, 8741, 2879, 46523, 572, 17706, 18554, 871, 19120, 11, 50645], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 266, "seek": 115314, "start": 1159.3600000000001, "end": 1162.26, "text": " digamos que um servidor prim\u00e1rio saia do ar,", "tokens": [50676, 36430, 631, 1105, 1658, 29718, 2886, 12657, 601, 654, 360, 594, 11, 50821], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 267, "seek": 115314, "start": 1162.66, "end": 1164.92, "text": " ou um link fundamental apodre\u00e7a.", "tokens": [50841, 2820, 1105, 2113, 8088, 1882, 378, 265, 5297, 13, 50954], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 268, "seek": 115314, "start": 1165.94, "end": 1166.42, "text": " Acabou.", "tokens": [51005, 5097, 455, 263, 13, 51029], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 269, "seek": 115314, "start": 1166.66, "end": 1167.5800000000002, "text": " A rodovia trava.", "tokens": [51041, 316, 744, 2595, 11617, 16020, 13, 51087], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 270, "seek": 115314, "start": 1168.1000000000001, "end": 1168.8000000000002, "text": " Ningu\u00e9m passa.", "tokens": [51113, 426, 25985, 23880, 13, 51148], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 271, "seek": 115314, "start": 1169.0800000000002, "end": 1172.5400000000002, "text": " O outro lado do conhecimento simplesmente desaparece.", "tokens": [51162, 422, 13170, 11631, 360, 15440, 28317, 44482, 42316, 384, 13, 51335], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 272, "seek": 115314, "start": 1172.66, "end": 1175.8400000000001, "text": " E qual a diferen\u00e7a para essas comunidades tradicionais?", "tokens": [51341, 462, 4101, 257, 38336, 1690, 19277, 11040, 10284, 2479, 18899, 1527, 30, 51500], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14898920059204102, "compression_ratio": 1.4278846153846154, "no_speech_prob": 1.0585287854580905e-11}, {"id": 273, "seek": 117584, "start": 1175.84, "end": 1180.98, "text": " Elas funcionam como uma rede de centenas de pequenas trilhas de terra.", "tokens": [50365, 2699, 296, 14186, 335, 2617, 2772, 14328, 368, 1489, 11581, 368, 26758, 11581, 26120, 12438, 368, 26298, 13, 50622], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 274, "seek": 117584, "start": 1181.34, "end": 1183.3, "text": " Uma rede org\u00e2nica espalhada.", "tokens": [50640, 21939, 14328, 14045, 9667, 2262, 7089, 304, 71, 1538, 13, 50738], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 275, "seek": 117584, "start": 1183.4399999999998, "end": 1185.72, "text": " Essa analogia \u00e9 perfeita.", "tokens": [50745, 22818, 16660, 654, 1136, 680, 2106, 2786, 13, 50859], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 276, "seek": 117584, "start": 1186.0, "end": 1189.08, "text": " A beleza topol\u00f3gica dessa rede de trilhas", "tokens": [50873, 316, 46429, 1192, 27629, 2262, 18554, 14328, 368, 26120, 12438, 51027], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 277, "seek": 117584, "start": 1189.08, "end": 1192.76, "text": " \u00e9 que se uma tempestade bloqueia uma trilha,", "tokens": [51027, 1136, 631, 369, 2772, 18274, 377, 762, 41592, 654, 2772, 26120, 1641, 11, 51211], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 278, "seek": 117584, "start": 1193.1799999999998, "end": 1197.5, "text": " as pessoas simplesmente d\u00e3o a volta usando a trilha do lado.", "tokens": [51232, 382, 10021, 44482, 274, 1076, 257, 18765, 29798, 257, 26120, 1641, 360, 11631, 13, 51448], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 279, "seek": 117584, "start": 1198.02, "end": 1202.5, "text": " O artigo chama isso de densidade redundante de caminhos.", "tokens": [51474, 422, 1523, 7483, 40954, 4616, 368, 24505, 6014, 27830, 2879, 368, 1945, 29140, 13, 51698], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 280, "seek": 117584, "start": 1203.36, "end": 1204.9199999999998, "text": " Densidade redundante.", "tokens": [51741, 413, 694, 6014, 27830, 2879, 13, 51819], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13875318647504928, "compression_ratio": 1.600896860986547, "no_speech_prob": 9.714457537002286e-12}, {"id": 281, "seek": 120492, "start": 1204.92, "end": 1209.1200000000001, "text": " \u00c9 ter v\u00e1rias rotas apontando para o mesmo lugar.", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 1796, 30235, 4297, 296, 1882, 896, 1806, 1690, 277, 9082, 11467, 13, 50575], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 282, "seek": 120492, "start": 1209.44, "end": 1210.0600000000002, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [50591, 2111, 2513, 13, 50622], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 283, "seek": 120492, "start": 1210.64, "end": 1214.9, "text": " Essas comunidades ancoram o conhecimento delas na tradi\u00e7\u00e3o oral,", "tokens": [50651, 14357, 296, 11040, 10284, 9789, 284, 335, 277, 15440, 28317, 1103, 296, 1667, 2479, 16661, 19338, 11, 50864], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 284, "seek": 120492, "start": 1215.66, "end": 1218.76, "text": " em rituais que se repetem periodicamente,", "tokens": [50902, 846, 367, 6380, 1527, 631, 369, 13645, 443, 2896, 23653, 11, 51057], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 285, "seek": 120492, "start": 1219.7, "end": 1222.72, "text": " na pr\u00f3pria arquitetura das ruas do bairro,", "tokens": [51104, 1667, 39608, 40258, 16341, 2991, 1482, 5420, 296, 360, 272, 1246, 340, 11, 51255], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 286, "seek": 120492, "start": 1223.26, "end": 1226.94, "text": " nas narrativas que os mais velhos passam para os mais novos.", "tokens": [51282, 5382, 6397, 35725, 631, 3003, 2420, 14610, 17631, 1320, 335, 1690, 3003, 2420, 572, 19140, 13, 51466], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 287, "seek": 120492, "start": 1227.24, "end": 1231.8400000000001, "text": " Se o portador de um peda\u00e7o espec\u00edfico dessa mem\u00f3ria falece,", "tokens": [51481, 1100, 277, 2436, 5409, 368, 1105, 5670, 64, 8560, 32741, 78, 18554, 1334, 15250, 26772, 384, 11, 51711], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 288, "seek": 120492, "start": 1231.8400000000001, "end": 1234.5, "text": " o sistema n\u00e3o desaba junto com ele.", "tokens": [51711, 277, 13245, 2431, 730, 5509, 24663, 395, 1118, 13, 51844], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12924729860745943, "compression_ratio": 1.4959677419354838, "no_speech_prob": 9.34160474669321e-12}, {"id": 289, "seek": 123450, "start": 1234.5, "end": 1238.44, "text": " N\u00e3o, porque existem dezenas de outras rotas,", "tokens": [50365, 8010, 11, 4021, 44345, 368, 2904, 296, 368, 22221, 4297, 296, 11, 50562], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1505745908488398, "compression_ratio": 1.2727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 8.114902846911853e-12}, {"id": 290, "seek": 123450, "start": 1239.26, "end": 1245.2, "text": " outras pessoas e rituais apontando para aquele mesmo significado compartilhado.", "tokens": [50603, 22221, 10021, 308, 367, 6380, 1527, 1882, 896, 1806, 1690, 23640, 9082, 3350, 1573, 40204, 71, 1573, 13, 50900], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1505745908488398, "compression_ratio": 1.2727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 8.114902846911853e-12}, {"id": 291, "seek": 123450, "start": 1245.56, "end": 1247.76, "text": " A redund\u00e2ncia salva a rede.", "tokens": [50918, 316, 27830, 25677, 1845, 2757, 257, 14328, 13, 51028], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1505745908488398, "compression_ratio": 1.2727272727272727, "no_speech_prob": 8.114902846911853e-12}, {"id": 292, "seek": 124776, "start": 1247.76, "end": 1256.42, "text": " A descentraliza\u00e7\u00e3o extrema de como a gente percorre o caminho compensa a falta de um grande HD central.", "tokens": [50365, 316, 23475, 2155, 27467, 1279, 265, 1696, 368, 2617, 257, 3788, 680, 19558, 265, 277, 37215, 11598, 64, 257, 22111, 368, 1105, 8883, 12149, 5777, 13, 50798], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10672009193291099, "compression_ratio": 1.345679012345679, "no_speech_prob": 8.808654326786236e-12}, {"id": 293, "seek": 124776, "start": 1257.42, "end": 1264.96, "text": " N\u00f3s terceirizamos a navega\u00e7\u00e3o inteira da nossa vida digital para duas ou tr\u00eas ferramentas de busca gigantes.", "tokens": [50848, 27626, 41385, 347, 590, 2151, 257, 39376, 3680, 2917, 2830, 4271, 1120, 15821, 7644, 4562, 1690, 19463, 2820, 20779, 7202, 44764, 296, 368, 37492, 8741, 9327, 13, 51225], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10672009193291099, "compression_ratio": 1.345679012345679, "no_speech_prob": 8.808654326786236e-12}, {"id": 294, "seek": 126496, "start": 1264.96, "end": 1269.96, "text": " Ficamos r\u00e1pidos, sim, mas ficamos incrivelmente fr\u00e1geis.", "tokens": [50365, 479, 299, 2151, 18213, 7895, 11, 1034, 11, 2300, 14591, 2151, 834, 470, 39786, 431, 842, 432, 271, 13, 50615], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15408215378270004, "compression_ratio": 1.0, "no_speech_prob": 1.0422281093713792e-11}, {"id": 295, "seek": 126496, "start": 1270.1200000000001, "end": 1271.6200000000001, "text": " \u00c9 um castelo de cartas.", "tokens": [50623, 4922, 1105, 4193, 10590, 368, 5467, 296, 13, 50698], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15408215378270004, "compression_ratio": 1.0, "no_speech_prob": 1.0422281093713792e-11}, {"id": 296, "seek": 127162, "start": 1271.62, "end": 1282.4199999999998, "text": " E essa an\u00e1lise fascinante da resist\u00eancia ao longo do tempo nos prepara para examinar o maior sistema de informa\u00e7\u00e3o j\u00e1 criado pela uma idade,", "tokens": [50365, 462, 7208, 44113, 908, 7184, 259, 2879, 1120, 4597, 9322, 8130, 40558, 360, 8972, 3269, 8231, 64, 1690, 1139, 6470, 277, 15859, 13245, 368, 48403, 6242, 12815, 1573, 14820, 2772, 4496, 762, 11, 50905], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09570153802633286, "compression_ratio": 1.4201183431952662, "no_speech_prob": 9.126052344377023e-12}, {"id": 297, "seek": 127162, "start": 1282.9599999999998, "end": 1289.6799999999998, "text": " aquele que n\u00e3o opera na escala de anos ou d\u00e9cadas, mas sim de mil\u00eanios, os idiomas humanos.", "tokens": [50932, 23640, 631, 2431, 22202, 1667, 4721, 5159, 368, 13592, 2820, 9198, 6872, 11, 2300, 1034, 368, 1962, 5050, 2717, 11, 3003, 18014, 7092, 34555, 13, 51268], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09570153802633286, "compression_ratio": 1.4201183431952662, "no_speech_prob": 9.126052344377023e-12}, {"id": 298, "seek": 128968, "start": 1289.68, "end": 1290.78, "text": " Sem d\u00favida.", "tokens": [50365, 14421, 39299, 32500, 13, 50420], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11529287099838256, "compression_ratio": 1.3833333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 9.019729407810928e-12}, {"id": 299, "seek": 128968, "start": 1291.52, "end": 1293.98, "text": " \u00c9 a cartada final da an\u00e1lise do autor.", "tokens": [50457, 4922, 257, 5467, 1538, 2572, 1120, 44113, 908, 360, 19510, 13, 50580], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11529287099838256, "compression_ratio": 1.3833333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 9.019729407810928e-12}, {"id": 300, "seek": 128968, "start": 1294.64, "end": 1299.4, "text": " Ele prop\u00f5e que a gente enxergue o idioma muito al\u00e9m do seu papel utilit\u00e1rio,", "tokens": [50613, 8024, 2365, 5536, 68, 631, 257, 3788, 465, 87, 260, 11929, 277, 18014, 6440, 4945, 30388, 360, 7986, 24710, 4976, 270, 12657, 11, 50851], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11529287099838256, "compression_ratio": 1.3833333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 9.019729407810928e-12}, {"id": 301, "seek": 128968, "start": 1299.92, "end": 1302.74, "text": " dessa comunica\u00e7\u00e3o di\u00e1ria que a gente est\u00e1 tendo aqui.", "tokens": [50877, 18554, 11040, 37823, 1026, 31861, 631, 257, 3788, 3192, 3928, 78, 3871, 13, 51018], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11529287099838256, "compression_ratio": 1.3833333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 9.019729407810928e-12}, {"id": 302, "seek": 128968, "start": 1303.1000000000001, "end": 1306.3600000000001, "text": " T\u00e1, e o que seria um idioma, ent\u00e3o, na vis\u00e3o de redes?", "tokens": [51036, 20907, 11, 308, 277, 631, 20809, 1105, 18014, 6440, 11, 9071, 11, 1667, 49949, 368, 16762, 30, 51199], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11529287099838256, "compression_ratio": 1.3833333333333333, "no_speech_prob": 9.019729407810928e-12}, {"id": 303, "seek": 130636, "start": 1306.36, "end": 1311.36, "text": " Um idioma \u00e9 um mapa de navega\u00e7\u00e3o imenso para um campo sem\u00e2ntico.", "tokens": [50365, 3301, 18014, 6440, 1136, 1105, 44025, 368, 39376, 3680, 2917, 566, 268, 539, 1690, 1105, 29691, 4361, 3201, 580, 2789, 13, 50615], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09782989819844563, "compression_ratio": 1.5169491525423728, "no_speech_prob": 7.989125853924417e-12}, {"id": 304, "seek": 130636, "start": 1312.4399999999998, "end": 1320.78, "text": " Aprender e manter um idioma vivo significa, na pr\u00e1tica, manter acess\u00edveis as chaves de leitura para tradi\u00e7\u00f5es inteiras.", "tokens": [50669, 316, 3712, 20535, 308, 48170, 1105, 18014, 6440, 30689, 19957, 11, 1667, 582, 23432, 11, 48170, 696, 442, 34934, 382, 417, 5423, 368, 476, 270, 2991, 1690, 2479, 38038, 2830, 23342, 13, 51086], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09782989819844563, "compression_ratio": 1.5169491525423728, "no_speech_prob": 7.989125853924417e-12}, {"id": 305, "seek": 130636, "start": 1321.62, "end": 1327.6999999999998, "text": " Quando uma l\u00edngua desaparece ou quando uma nova l\u00edngua \u00e9 imposta, n\u00e3o \u00e9 s\u00f3 uma troca de dicion\u00e1rio.", "tokens": [51128, 18725, 2772, 16118, 872, 4398, 42316, 384, 2820, 7770, 2772, 28265, 16118, 872, 4398, 1136, 704, 8638, 11, 2431, 1136, 6238, 2772, 4495, 496, 368, 14285, 313, 12657, 13, 51432], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09782989819844563, "compression_ratio": 1.5169491525423728, "no_speech_prob": 7.989125853924417e-12}, {"id": 306, "seek": 130636, "start": 1328.1399999999999, "end": 1331.86, "text": " \u00c9 uma reconfigura\u00e7\u00e3o massiva da infraestrutura de rede.", "tokens": [51454, 4922, 2772, 9993, 20646, 2991, 2917, 2758, 5931, 1120, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 368, 14328, 13, 51640], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09782989819844563, "compression_ratio": 1.5169491525423728, "no_speech_prob": 7.989125853924417e-12}, {"id": 307, "seek": 133186, "start": 1331.86, "end": 1337.4799999999998, "text": " Nossa, isso fica muito evidente quando a gente analisa movimentos hist\u00f3ricos profundos.", "tokens": [50365, 36016, 11, 4616, 16868, 4945, 16371, 68, 7770, 257, 3788, 2624, 3837, 2402, 34626, 33196, 1341, 329, 1740, 36518, 13, 50646], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 308, "seek": 133186, "start": 1338.1399999999999, "end": 1343.1599999999999, "text": " Podemos observar, por exemplo, o momento em que o idioma franc\u00eas padronizado", "tokens": [50679, 12646, 4485, 9951, 289, 11, 1515, 16496, 11, 277, 9333, 846, 631, 277, 18014, 6440, 30514, 11987, 6887, 2044, 27441, 50930], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 309, "seek": 133186, "start": 1343.1599999999999, "end": 1347.6399999999999, "text": " substituiu os diversos dialetos regionais l\u00e1 na Fran\u00e7a.", "tokens": [50930, 26441, 3077, 84, 3003, 6111, 329, 5502, 49476, 4458, 1527, 7453, 1667, 17288, 5297, 13, 51154], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 310, "seek": 133186, "start": 1347.6999999999998, "end": 1349.76, "text": " Aham, os patois locais.", "tokens": [51157, 2438, 335, 11, 3003, 1947, 7376, 47965, 271, 13, 51260], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 311, "seek": 133186, "start": 1350.1, "end": 1350.4799999999998, "text": " Isso.", "tokens": [51277, 14887, 13, 51296], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 312, "seek": 133186, "start": 1350.82, "end": 1359.26, "text": " Ou como a l\u00edngua inglesa reconfigurou territ\u00f3rios globais gigantescos devido ao processo hist\u00f3rico do colonialismo.", "tokens": [51313, 11710, 2617, 257, 16118, 872, 4398, 3957, 904, 64, 9993, 20646, 374, 263, 8673, 812, 37994, 16125, 1527, 8741, 9327, 6877, 1905, 2925, 8130, 27939, 33196, 23776, 360, 19066, 6882, 13, 51735], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.0957951073174004, "compression_ratio": 1.4743083003952568, "no_speech_prob": 9.487220904713656e-12}, {"id": 313, "seek": 135926, "start": 1359.26, "end": 1368.78, "text": " Ou a forma como o espanhol alterou completamente os sistemas complexos de conhecimento que j\u00e1 existiam na Mesoam\u00e9rica.", "tokens": [50365, 11710, 257, 8366, 2617, 277, 785, 6040, 5449, 11337, 263, 28381, 3003, 48720, 3997, 329, 368, 15440, 28317, 631, 6242, 2514, 2918, 1667, 17485, 78, 335, 32716, 13, 50841], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10470402759054433, "compression_ratio": 1.5068493150684932, "no_speech_prob": 8.879951461648883e-12}, {"id": 314, "seek": 135926, "start": 1369.0, "end": 1374.64, "text": " E \u00e9 importante frisar que o autor analisa isso tudo de forma bem imparcial,", "tokens": [50852, 462, 1136, 9416, 431, 271, 289, 631, 277, 19510, 2624, 3837, 4616, 9379, 368, 8366, 7577, 704, 289, 1013, 11, 51134], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10470402759054433, "compression_ratio": 1.5068493150684932, "no_speech_prob": 8.879951461648883e-12}, {"id": 315, "seek": 135926, "start": 1374.94, "end": 1378.74, "text": " apenas pela \u00f3tica puramente estrutural da teoria das redes.", "tokens": [51149, 18561, 14820, 44490, 2262, 1864, 3439, 45899, 1807, 1120, 535, 8172, 1482, 16762, 13, 51339], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10470402759054433, "compression_ratio": 1.5068493150684932, "no_speech_prob": 8.879951461648883e-12}, {"id": 316, "seek": 135926, "start": 1379.18, "end": 1379.84, "text": " Exatamente.", "tokens": [51361, 2111, 25354, 13, 51394], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10470402759054433, "compression_ratio": 1.5068493150684932, "no_speech_prob": 8.879951461648883e-12}, {"id": 317, "seek": 135926, "start": 1380.54, "end": 1384.62, "text": " Sem ju\u00edzo de valor pol\u00edtico na an\u00e1lise estrutural em si.", "tokens": [51429, 14421, 3649, 870, 4765, 368, 15367, 48641, 1667, 44113, 908, 45899, 1807, 846, 1511, 13, 51633], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10470402759054433, "compression_ratio": 1.5068493150684932, "no_speech_prob": 8.879951461648883e-12}, {"id": 318, "seek": 138462, "start": 1384.62, "end": 1389.02, "text": " O efeito mec\u00e2nico da mudan\u00e7a de idioma \u00e9 implac\u00e1vel.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 308, 35417, 25186, 9667, 2789, 1120, 8933, 22930, 368, 18014, 6440, 1136, 8484, 326, 20224, 13, 50585], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 319, "seek": 138462, "start": 1389.6399999999999, "end": 1392.8999999999999, "text": " Os hiperlinks para as tradi\u00e7\u00f5es antigas s\u00e3o cortados,", "tokens": [50616, 8875, 4879, 610, 75, 16431, 1690, 382, 2479, 38038, 44417, 296, 8364, 11278, 4181, 11, 50779], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 320, "seek": 138462, "start": 1393.52, "end": 1398.6599999999999, "text": " mesmo que os c\u00f3digos ou, sei l\u00e1, os textos em pedra sobrevivam fisicamente.", "tokens": [50810, 9082, 631, 3003, 40210, 13348, 2820, 11, 10842, 7453, 11, 3003, 2487, 329, 846, 5670, 424, 5473, 27810, 335, 36609, 23653, 13, 51067], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 321, "seek": 138462, "start": 1399.02, "end": 1403.84, "text": " A capacidade das pessoas de alcan\u00e7\u00e1-los mentalmente \u00e9 destru\u00edda.", "tokens": [51085, 316, 4637, 6014, 1482, 10021, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 842, 12, 9389, 4973, 4082, 1136, 34235, 39080, 13, 51326], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 322, "seek": 138462, "start": 1404.04, "end": 1409.04, "text": " O texto em pedra se torna um documento perfeitamente preservado,", "tokens": [51336, 422, 35503, 846, 5670, 424, 369, 3930, 629, 1105, 4166, 78, 680, 37434, 3439, 45905, 1573, 11, 51586], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 323, "seek": 138462, "start": 1409.6, "end": 1412.6599999999999, "text": " por\u00e9m ileg\u00edvel em um servidor desconectado.", "tokens": [51614, 1515, 4011, 741, 6363, 13185, 846, 1105, 1658, 29718, 7471, 546, 349, 1573, 13, 51767], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07351046342116135, "compression_ratio": 1.4780876494023905, "no_speech_prob": 9.451641726221371e-12}, {"id": 324, "seek": 141266, "start": 1412.66, "end": 1418.8200000000002, "text": " A ponte cai, mas o inverso tamb\u00e9m ocorre de forma bem not\u00e1vel, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [50365, 316, 280, 10219, 46523, 11, 2300, 277, 28653, 539, 6274, 10409, 284, 265, 368, 8366, 7577, 406, 20224, 11, 7024, 30, 50673], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 325, "seek": 141266, "start": 1419.0400000000002, "end": 1419.8000000000002, "text": " Com certeza.", "tokens": [50684, 2432, 30424, 13, 50722], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 326, "seek": 141266, "start": 1420.02, "end": 1427.6000000000001, "text": " O artigo traz o idioma \u00e1rabe como um dos maiores exemplos de alcan\u00e7abilidade j\u00e1 documentados na hist\u00f3ria.", "tokens": [50733, 422, 1523, 7483, 37481, 277, 18014, 6440, 7352, 424, 650, 2617, 1105, 4491, 12698, 2706, 24112, 329, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 6242, 4166, 4181, 1667, 20670, 13, 51112], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 327, "seek": 141266, "start": 1427.92, "end": 1431.52, "text": " 14 s\u00e9culos de alcan\u00e7abilidade cont\u00ednua.", "tokens": [51128, 3499, 7910, 32397, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 660, 10973, 4398, 13, 51308], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 328, "seek": 141266, "start": 1431.74, "end": 1432.64, "text": " \u00c9 muita coisa.", "tokens": [51319, 4922, 21025, 9614, 13, 51364], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 329, "seek": 141266, "start": 1432.8600000000001, "end": 1433.78, "text": " Muita coisa.", "tokens": [51375, 376, 1983, 64, 9614, 13, 51421], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11268387483746818, "compression_ratio": 1.3894736842105264, "no_speech_prob": 8.983839713816444e-12}, {"id": 330, "seek": 143378, "start": 1433.78, "end": 1439.16, "text": " Atrav\u00e9s de imp\u00e9rios caindo, guerras, enormes dispers\u00f5es pelo mundo,", "tokens": [50365, 1711, 13404, 2191, 368, 704, 12052, 329, 1335, 10306, 11, 14486, 3906, 11, 8473, 279, 24631, 6036, 12167, 7968, 11, 50634], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09780542585584852, "compression_ratio": 1.4174757281553398, "no_speech_prob": 1.0917339081373267e-11}, {"id": 331, "seek": 143378, "start": 1439.68, "end": 1445.06, "text": " a estrutura do \u00e1rabe manteve o acesso livre aos seus textos cl\u00e1ssicos.", "tokens": [50660, 257, 45899, 2991, 360, 7352, 424, 650, 275, 2879, 303, 277, 49543, 24735, 25458, 17004, 2487, 329, 47434, 82, 9940, 13, 50929], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09780542585584852, "compression_ratio": 1.4174757281553398, "no_speech_prob": 1.0917339081373267e-11}, {"id": 332, "seek": 143378, "start": 1445.66, "end": 1453.52, "text": " E a engenharia, por tr\u00e1s disso, dependeu justamente daquela trilha de terra redundante que a gente conversou.", "tokens": [50959, 462, 257, 1741, 268, 5854, 654, 11, 1515, 46189, 20088, 11, 1367, 36202, 41056, 1120, 41462, 26120, 1641, 368, 26298, 27830, 2879, 631, 257, 3788, 2615, 263, 13, 51352], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09780542585584852, "compression_ratio": 1.4174757281553398, "no_speech_prob": 1.0917339081373267e-11}, {"id": 333, "seek": 143378, "start": 1453.6, "end": 1456.18, "text": " A memoriza\u00e7\u00e3o em massa, os rituais.", "tokens": [51356, 316, 10560, 27467, 846, 26689, 11, 3003, 367, 6380, 1527, 13, 51485], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09780542585584852, "compression_ratio": 1.4174757281553398, "no_speech_prob": 1.0917339081373267e-11}, {"id": 334, "seek": 145618, "start": 1456.18, "end": 1457.02, "text": " Exato.", "tokens": [50365, 2111, 2513, 13, 50407], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10366799550897934, "compression_ratio": 1.4339622641509433, "no_speech_prob": 1.153610800636029e-11}, {"id": 335, "seek": 145618, "start": 1457.16, "end": 1464.48, "text": " A repeti\u00e7\u00e3o lit\u00fargica cont\u00ednua, uma educa\u00e7\u00e3o cl\u00e1ssica que n\u00e3o apenas guarda o livro na estante,", "tokens": [50414, 316, 13645, 16661, 7997, 2481, 81, 70, 2262, 660, 10973, 4398, 11, 2772, 1257, 32072, 2917, 47434, 82, 2262, 631, 2431, 18561, 6290, 64, 277, 33545, 1667, 871, 2879, 11, 50780], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10366799550897934, "compression_ratio": 1.4339622641509433, "no_speech_prob": 1.153610800636029e-11}, {"id": 336, "seek": 145618, "start": 1464.8, "end": 1473.88, "text": " mas recita em voz alta e s\u00e9culos e s\u00e9culos ininterruptos de coment\u00e1rios acad\u00eamicos sobre coment\u00e1rios anteriores.", "tokens": [50796, 2300, 850, 2786, 846, 30005, 26495, 308, 7910, 32397, 308, 7910, 32397, 294, 5106, 5428, 329, 368, 43739, 5558, 13213, 9940, 5473, 43739, 364, 34345, 2706, 13, 51250], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10366799550897934, "compression_ratio": 1.4339622641509433, "no_speech_prob": 1.153610800636029e-11}, {"id": 337, "seek": 147388, "start": 1473.88, "end": 1481.88, "text": " Ent\u00e3o, nesse caso, o significado daquelas ideias nunca foi um objeto trancado num cofre.", "tokens": [50365, 6469, 11, 18270, 9666, 11, 277, 3350, 1573, 1120, 20593, 296, 1153, 4609, 13768, 6901, 1105, 40438, 504, 4463, 1573, 1031, 598, 19325, 13, 50765], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 338, "seek": 147388, "start": 1482.64, "end": 1488.5200000000002, "text": " Foi uma rota, uma trilha repetidamente caminhada por milh\u00f5es e milh\u00f5es de pessoas ao longo do tempo.", "tokens": [50803, 30995, 2772, 4297, 64, 11, 2772, 26120, 1641, 13645, 49663, 1945, 10085, 1538, 1515, 39252, 308, 39252, 368, 10021, 8130, 40558, 360, 8972, 13, 51097], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 339, "seek": 147388, "start": 1488.94, "end": 1491.0400000000002, "text": " Caminhada e recaminhada.", "tokens": [51118, 6886, 10085, 1538, 308, 850, 7428, 71, 1538, 13, 51223], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 340, "seek": 147388, "start": 1491.4, "end": 1493.38, "text": " \u00c9 isso que mant\u00e9m a aresta viva.", "tokens": [51241, 4922, 4616, 631, 10845, 4011, 257, 366, 9140, 371, 5931, 13, 51340], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 341, "seek": 147388, "start": 1493.68, "end": 1495.96, "text": " Isso que tudo isso significa na pr\u00e1tica.", "tokens": [51355, 14887, 631, 9379, 4616, 19957, 1667, 582, 23432, 13, 51469], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 342, "seek": 147388, "start": 1496.5800000000002, "end": 1501.68, "text": " Especialmente se a gente trouxer essa lente anal\u00edtica para a gest\u00e3o p\u00fablica contempor\u00e2nea,", "tokens": [51500, 2313, 494, 1013, 4082, 369, 257, 3788, 3455, 87, 260, 7208, 287, 1576, 2624, 6712, 2262, 1690, 257, 7219, 1076, 38905, 13046, 3201, 22160, 11, 51755], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09244370460510254, "compression_ratio": 1.5877551020408163, "no_speech_prob": 8.40746482849708e-12}, {"id": 343, "seek": 150168, "start": 1501.68, "end": 1505.68, "text": " para a pol\u00edtica de hoje, o autor cita um caso institucional intrigante,", "tokens": [50365, 1690, 257, 25029, 368, 13458, 11, 277, 19510, 269, 2786, 1105, 9666, 4348, 1311, 1966, 17934, 2879, 11, 50565], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 344, "seek": 150168, "start": 1506.8, "end": 1508.68, "text": " que \u00e9 a famosa Carta da L\u00edngua Francesa.", "tokens": [50621, 631, 1136, 257, 1087, 6447, 383, 19061, 1120, 441, 870, 872, 4398, 31441, 64, 13, 50715], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 345, "seek": 150168, "start": 1509.6200000000001, "end": 1517.8600000000001, "text": " Sim, a Charte de la Lange Fran\u00e7aise, promulgada em Quebec no final dos anos 70, em 1977.", "tokens": [50762, 3998, 11, 257, 761, 11026, 368, 635, 441, 933, 17288, 5297, 908, 11, 2234, 425, 70, 1538, 846, 38903, 572, 2572, 4491, 13592, 5285, 11, 846, 35092, 13, 51174], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 346, "seek": 150168, "start": 1518.78, "end": 1519.14, "text": " Isso.", "tokens": [51220, 14887, 13, 51238], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 347, "seek": 150168, "start": 1519.88, "end": 1523.78, "text": " Geralmente, quando a gente v\u00ea pol\u00edticas p\u00fablicas desse tipo rolando pelo mundo,", "tokens": [51275, 48527, 4082, 11, 7770, 257, 3788, 30384, 45931, 15392, 296, 17864, 9746, 744, 16201, 12167, 7968, 11, 51470], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 348, "seek": 150168, "start": 1524.24, "end": 1528.04, "text": " a gente as encara puramente como movimentos de orgulho identit\u00e1rio,", "tokens": [51493, 257, 3788, 382, 47287, 1864, 3439, 2617, 2402, 34626, 368, 14045, 425, 1289, 2473, 270, 12657, 11, 51683], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 349, "seek": 150168, "start": 1528.44, "end": 1529.92, "text": " sabe, de preserva\u00e7\u00e3o cultural.", "tokens": [51703, 12275, 11, 368, 45905, 6670, 6988, 13, 51777], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1624923865000407, "compression_ratio": 1.4612546125461254, "no_speech_prob": 9.829423733287435e-12}, {"id": 350, "seek": 152992, "start": 1529.92, "end": 1535.04, "text": " Onde \u00e9 que a topologia de redes de computadores entra numa legisla\u00e7\u00e3o assim?", "tokens": [50365, 422, 16404, 1136, 631, 257, 1192, 24103, 368, 16762, 368, 2807, 11856, 22284, 29080, 1676, 271, 875, 2917, 8249, 30, 50621], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 351, "seek": 152992, "start": 1535.04, "end": 1539.28, "text": " Entra na compreens\u00e3o genial da mec\u00e2nica do atrito na rede.", "tokens": [50621, 3951, 424, 1667, 715, 9098, 1076, 48228, 1120, 25186, 9667, 2262, 360, 412, 17492, 1667, 14328, 13, 50833], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 352, "seek": 152992, "start": 1540.02, "end": 1545.72, "text": " Quando a lei de Quebec exige que as grandes empresas, o com\u00e9rcio e a educa\u00e7\u00e3o", "tokens": [50870, 18725, 257, 32791, 368, 38903, 454, 3969, 631, 382, 16640, 26433, 11, 277, 395, 4198, 8529, 308, 257, 1257, 32072, 2917, 51155], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 353, "seek": 152992, "start": 1545.72, "end": 1548.04, "text": " operem estritamente em franc\u00eas,", "tokens": [51155, 999, 7333, 871, 3210, 3439, 846, 30514, 11987, 11, 51271], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 354, "seek": 152992, "start": 1548.6200000000001, "end": 1552.8400000000001, "text": " ela funciona tecnicamente como uma restri\u00e7\u00e3o de alcan\u00e7abilidade.", "tokens": [51300, 7175, 26210, 535, 66, 7692, 3439, 2617, 2772, 1472, 470, 2917, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 13, 51511], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 355, "seek": 152992, "start": 1553.22, "end": 1556.96, "text": " Hum, uma restri\u00e7\u00e3o de alcan\u00e7abilidade?", "tokens": [51530, 12877, 11, 2772, 1472, 470, 2917, 368, 419, 7035, 1138, 5177, 6014, 30, 51717], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826157024928502, "compression_ratio": 1.6621004566210045, "no_speech_prob": 8.114971368489154e-12}, {"id": 356, "seek": 155696, "start": 1556.96, "end": 1561.82, "text": " Sim, ela cria uma condi\u00e7\u00e3o de contorno jur\u00eddica, uma barreira,", "tokens": [50365, 3998, 11, 7175, 269, 4668, 2772, 2224, 16661, 368, 660, 21998, 12721, 24455, 2262, 11, 2772, 43834, 4271, 11, 50608], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09202455338977632, "compression_ratio": 1.4126984126984128, "no_speech_prob": 8.506429935439819e-12}, {"id": 357, "seek": 155696, "start": 1562.3400000000001, "end": 1566.06, "text": " for\u00e7ando a manuten\u00e7\u00e3o cont\u00ednua das arestas lingu\u00edsticas.", "tokens": [50634, 337, 1138, 1806, 257, 587, 7886, 2917, 660, 10973, 4398, 1482, 366, 372, 296, 21766, 19512, 9150, 13, 50820], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09202455338977632, "compression_ratio": 1.4126984126984128, "no_speech_prob": 8.506429935439819e-12}, {"id": 358, "seek": 155696, "start": 1566.7, "end": 1572.32, "text": " Pensa na gravidade econ\u00f4mica e corporativa massiva da Am\u00e9rica do Norte ditando as regras.", "tokens": [50852, 430, 23364, 1667, 7427, 6014, 23692, 25670, 2262, 308, 6804, 18740, 2758, 5931, 1120, 48053, 360, 426, 12752, 6176, 1806, 382, 319, 861, 296, 13, 51133], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09202455338977632, "compression_ratio": 1.4126984126984128, "no_speech_prob": 8.506429935439819e-12}, {"id": 359, "seek": 155696, "start": 1572.48, "end": 1575.4, "text": " \u00c9 uma press\u00e3o enorme do ingl\u00eas o tempo todo.", "tokens": [51141, 4922, 2772, 1886, 1076, 33648, 360, 35511, 11987, 277, 8972, 5149, 13, 51287], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09202455338977632, "compression_ratio": 1.4126984126984128, "no_speech_prob": 8.506429935439819e-12}, {"id": 360, "seek": 157540, "start": 1575.4, "end": 1581.6000000000001, "text": " Exato. Sob essa press\u00e3o do mercado, a tend\u00eancia natural de menor resist\u00eancia", "tokens": [50365, 2111, 2513, 13, 407, 65, 7208, 1886, 1076, 360, 24775, 11, 257, 3928, 9322, 3303, 368, 26343, 4597, 9322, 50675], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07561321747608674, "compression_ratio": 1.417989417989418, "no_speech_prob": 1.0061357129387272e-11}, {"id": 361, "seek": 157540, "start": 1581.6000000000001, "end": 1585.94, "text": " seria que os caminhos em franc\u00eas apodrecessem por falta de uso di\u00e1rio,", "tokens": [50675, 20809, 631, 3003, 1945, 29140, 846, 30514, 11987, 1882, 378, 265, 887, 19872, 1515, 22111, 368, 22728, 1026, 12657, 11, 50892], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07561321747608674, "compression_ratio": 1.417989417989418, "no_speech_prob": 1.0061357129387272e-11}, {"id": 362, "seek": 157540, "start": 1586.18, "end": 1589.96, "text": " assim como aqueles links num site desatualizado que a gente comentou.", "tokens": [50904, 8249, 2617, 49831, 6123, 1031, 3621, 730, 267, 901, 27441, 631, 257, 3788, 14541, 263, 13, 51093], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07561321747608674, "compression_ratio": 1.417989417989418, "no_speech_prob": 1.0061357129387272e-11}, {"id": 363, "seek": 157540, "start": 1590.1200000000001, "end": 1593.24, "text": " Eles iam parar de ser clicados, na vida real.", "tokens": [51101, 31096, 741, 335, 37193, 368, 816, 33661, 4181, 11, 1667, 7644, 957, 13, 51257], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07561321747608674, "compression_ratio": 1.417989417989418, "no_speech_prob": 1.0061357129387272e-11}, {"id": 364, "seek": 159324, "start": 1593.24, "end": 1602.1200000000001, "text": " Aham. Ent\u00e3o a legisla\u00e7\u00e3o atua como a manuten\u00e7\u00e3o peri\u00f3dica e obrigue desses hiperlinks culturais.", "tokens": [50365, 2438, 335, 13, 6469, 257, 1676, 271, 875, 2917, 412, 4398, 2617, 257, 587, 7886, 2917, 680, 7138, 67, 2262, 308, 1111, 7065, 622, 36409, 4879, 610, 75, 16431, 2376, 374, 1527, 13, 50809], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10380208610308052, "compression_ratio": 1.5255813953488373, "no_speech_prob": 1.0922204980723382e-11}, {"id": 365, "seek": 159324, "start": 1602.78, "end": 1608.16, "text": " Ela garante que o custo de transa\u00e7\u00e3o de usar o franc\u00eas n\u00e3o fique alto demais,", "tokens": [50842, 17637, 3691, 2879, 631, 277, 14884, 78, 368, 1145, 6670, 368, 14745, 277, 30514, 11987, 2431, 35497, 21275, 36879, 11, 51111], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10380208610308052, "compression_ratio": 1.5255813953488373, "no_speech_prob": 1.0922204980723382e-11}, {"id": 366, "seek": 159324, "start": 1608.34, "end": 1615.1, "text": " porque se ficar, a rede local inteira pode colapsar e ser sugada em dire\u00e7\u00e3o ao novezinho,", "tokens": [51120, 4021, 369, 13646, 11, 257, 14328, 2654, 2830, 4271, 7468, 1173, 2382, 289, 308, 816, 22802, 1538, 846, 1264, 2917, 8130, 26972, 31282, 11, 51458], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10380208610308052, "compression_ratio": 1.5255813953488373, "no_speech_prob": 1.0922204980723382e-11}, {"id": 367, "seek": 159324, "start": 1615.2, "end": 1618.02, "text": " que \u00e9 muito mais denso que seria o idioma ingl\u00eas.", "tokens": [51463, 631, 1136, 4945, 2420, 1441, 539, 631, 20809, 277, 18014, 6440, 35511, 11987, 13, 51604], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10380208610308052, "compression_ratio": 1.5255813953488373, "no_speech_prob": 1.0922204980723382e-11}, {"id": 368, "seek": 161802, "start": 1618.02, "end": 1626.32, "text": " Caramba. \u00c9 a mesm\u00edssima f\u00edsica que opera na queda e na ascens\u00e3o de grandes plataformas da internet,", "tokens": [50365, 2741, 23337, 13, 4922, 257, 3813, 76, 36375, 4775, 46436, 631, 22202, 1667, 23314, 308, 1667, 15526, 694, 1076, 368, 16640, 36448, 296, 1120, 4705, 11, 50780], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 369, "seek": 161802, "start": 1626.5, "end": 1633.06, "text": " s\u00f3 que rodando num sistema operacional formado por leis civis e intera\u00e7\u00f5es sociais di\u00e1rias nas ruas de Quebec.", "tokens": [50789, 6238, 631, 8685, 1806, 1031, 13245, 2208, 13608, 1254, 1573, 1515, 476, 271, 13779, 271, 308, 728, 17971, 45179, 1026, 24952, 5382, 5420, 296, 368, 38903, 13, 51117], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 370, "seek": 161802, "start": 1633.56, "end": 1634.62, "text": " \u00c9 fascinante.", "tokens": [51142, 4922, 7184, 259, 2879, 13, 51195], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 371, "seek": 161802, "start": 1634.8, "end": 1639.0, "text": " \u00c9 uma lente completamente nova pra olhar as pol\u00edticas lingu\u00edsticas, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51204, 4922, 2772, 287, 1576, 28381, 28265, 3206, 37446, 382, 45931, 21766, 19512, 9150, 11, 7024, 30, 51414], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 372, "seek": 161802, "start": 1639.1399999999999, "end": 1639.82, "text": " Com certeza.", "tokens": [51421, 2432, 30424, 13, 51455], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 373, "seek": 161802, "start": 1640.82, "end": 1645.6, "text": " Bom, juntando todas as pe\u00e7as dessa nossa longa travessia de hoje,", "tokens": [51505, 19812, 11, 22739, 1806, 10906, 382, 520, 20016, 18554, 15821, 938, 64, 11783, 442, 654, 368, 13458, 11, 51744], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10302662630693628, "compression_ratio": 1.501930501930502, "no_speech_prob": 8.776782252362114e-12}, {"id": 374, "seek": 164560, "start": 1645.6, "end": 1650.12, "text": " a gente foi desde f\u00f3runs online no Facebook, que mudam de nome do nada,", "tokens": [50365, 257, 3788, 6901, 10188, 283, 812, 12997, 82, 2950, 572, 4384, 11, 631, 8933, 335, 368, 19003, 360, 8096, 11, 50591], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 375, "seek": 164560, "start": 1650.56, "end": 1654.1799999999998, "text": " at\u00e9 o apodrecimento invis\u00edvel de links acad\u00eamicos", "tokens": [50613, 8784, 277, 1882, 378, 13867, 10030, 13308, 13185, 368, 6123, 5558, 13213, 9940, 50794], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 376, "seek": 164560, "start": 1654.1799999999998, "end": 1657.9199999999998, "text": " e a sobreviv\u00eancia \u00e9pica de idiomas antigos.", "tokens": [50794, 308, 257, 5473, 27810, 9322, 21018, 2262, 368, 18014, 7092, 2511, 13348, 13, 50981], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 377, "seek": 164560, "start": 1658.6, "end": 1660.6, "text": " A grande pergunta que fica pra n\u00f3s \u00e9", "tokens": [51015, 316, 8883, 34908, 631, 16868, 3206, 9738, 1136, 51115], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 378, "seek": 164560, "start": 1660.6, "end": 1663.62, "text": " como \u00e9 que a gente conserta essas pontes?", "tokens": [51115, 2617, 1136, 631, 257, 3788, 1014, 22765, 19277, 18770, 279, 30, 51266], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 379, "seek": 164560, "start": 1663.7199999999998, "end": 1666.3999999999999, "text": " \u00c9 o que todo mundo quer saber, n\u00e9?", "tokens": [51271, 4922, 277, 631, 5149, 7968, 7083, 12489, 11, 7024, 30, 51405], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 380, "seek": 164560, "start": 1666.6799999999998, "end": 1673.12, "text": " O Flaxleon n\u00e3o entrega apenas um diagn\u00f3stico apocal\u00edptico do fim da nossa mem\u00f3ria digital.", "tokens": [51419, 422, 479, 25923, 306, 266, 2431, 32843, 64, 18561, 1105, 7234, 45052, 2789, 1882, 36483, 870, 662, 2789, 360, 31603, 1120, 15821, 1334, 15250, 4562, 13, 51741], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12039987449972038, "compression_ratio": 1.4694656488549618, "no_speech_prob": 9.306022098753974e-12}, {"id": 381, "seek": 167312, "start": 1673.12, "end": 1680.9399999999998, "text": " Ele deixa no artigo o que ele descreve como o requisito construtivo da mem\u00f3ria do futuro.", "tokens": [50365, 8024, 26208, 572, 1523, 7483, 277, 631, 1118, 7471, 265, 303, 2617, 277, 49878, 3528, 1817, 24316, 6340, 1120, 1334, 15250, 360, 23953, 13, 50756], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 382, "seek": 167312, "start": 1681.2399999999998, "end": 1683.7399999999998, "text": " Um manual de instru\u00e7\u00f5es. O que ele diz?", "tokens": [50771, 3301, 9688, 368, 1058, 894, 8001, 13, 422, 631, 1118, 12098, 30, 50896], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 383, "seek": 167312, "start": 1684.02, "end": 1689.54, "text": " A solu\u00e7\u00e3o exige que a gente pare de pensar nessas coisas de forma separada", "tokens": [50910, 316, 24807, 2917, 454, 3969, 631, 257, 3788, 7448, 368, 18321, 39787, 296, 14567, 368, 8366, 3128, 1538, 51186], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 384, "seek": 167312, "start": 1689.54, "end": 1694.04, "text": " e adote tr\u00eas posturas simult\u00e2neas na nossa infraestrutura.", "tokens": [51186, 308, 614, 1370, 20779, 2183, 12907, 13899, 3201, 716, 296, 1667, 15821, 23654, 377, 24316, 2991, 13, 51411], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 385, "seek": 167312, "start": 1694.4599999999998, "end": 1697.32, "text": " A primeira \u00e9 a persist\u00eancia do n\u00f3.", "tokens": [51432, 316, 21158, 1136, 257, 13233, 9322, 360, 6604, 13, 51575], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 386, "seek": 167312, "start": 1697.8999999999999, "end": 1700.4799999999998, "text": " Isso \u00e9 o b\u00e1sico e a gente j\u00e1 faz super bem.", "tokens": [51604, 14887, 1136, 277, 25545, 2789, 308, 257, 3788, 6242, 4375, 1687, 7577, 13, 51733], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08605408891339168, "compression_ratio": 1.4730290456431536, "no_speech_prob": 9.63907686307719e-12}, {"id": 387, "seek": 170048, "start": 1700.48, "end": 1704.14, "text": " \u00c9 garantir que a informa\u00e7\u00e3o exista l\u00e1 fisicamente,", "tokens": [50365, 4922, 22251, 347, 631, 257, 48403, 2514, 64, 7453, 36609, 23653, 11, 50548], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 388, "seek": 170048, "start": 1704.52, "end": 1707.6, "text": " seja no HD, na nuvem ou no papel.", "tokens": [50567, 13459, 572, 12149, 11, 1667, 3822, 31651, 2820, 572, 24710, 13, 50721], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 389, "seek": 170048, "start": 1707.8600000000001, "end": 1709.8, "text": " Salvar o arquivo, basicamente.", "tokens": [50734, 5996, 8517, 277, 40258, 6340, 11, 3875, 3439, 13, 50831], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 390, "seek": 170048, "start": 1709.9, "end": 1710.3, "text": " Isso.", "tokens": [50836, 14887, 13, 50856], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 391, "seek": 170048, "start": 1710.8, "end": 1713.72, "text": " A segunda postura \u00e9 a manuten\u00e7\u00e3o da aresta.", "tokens": [50881, 316, 21978, 2183, 2991, 1136, 257, 587, 7886, 2917, 1120, 366, 9140, 13, 51027], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 392, "seek": 170048, "start": 1714.24, "end": 1715.9, "text": " O caminho at\u00e9 o arquivo,", "tokens": [51053, 422, 37215, 8784, 277, 40258, 6340, 11, 51136], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 393, "seek": 170048, "start": 1716.22, "end": 1717.8, "text": " seja um hiperlink na internet,", "tokens": [51152, 13459, 1105, 4879, 610, 22473, 1667, 4705, 11, 51231], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 394, "seek": 170048, "start": 1718.18, "end": 1720.04, "text": " uma tradi\u00e7\u00e3o oral contada,", "tokens": [51250, 2772, 2479, 16661, 19338, 660, 1538, 11, 51343], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 395, "seek": 170048, "start": 1720.14, "end": 1722.22, "text": " uma ficha num cat\u00e1logo f\u00edsico,", "tokens": [51348, 2772, 283, 48710, 1031, 3857, 842, 38212, 27538, 2789, 11, 51452], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 396, "seek": 170048, "start": 1722.74, "end": 1725.28, "text": " precisa ser continuamente limpo,", "tokens": [51478, 18861, 816, 2993, 3439, 2364, 2259, 11, 51605], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 397, "seek": 170048, "start": 1725.7, "end": 1727.54, "text": " verificado e desimpedido.", "tokens": [51626, 1306, 1089, 1573, 308, 730, 332, 3452, 2925, 13, 51718], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.15219896781344375, "compression_ratio": 1.4644351464435146, "no_speech_prob": 9.342550170987618e-12}, {"id": 398, "seek": 172754, "start": 1727.54, "end": 1730.58, "text": " O caminho precisa existir no presente.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 37215, 18861, 2514, 347, 572, 28709, 13, 50517], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 399, "seek": 172754, "start": 1730.58, "end": 1733.6, "text": " N\u00e3o adianta ter o link se o servidor desligou, claro.", "tokens": [50517, 8010, 614, 5798, 64, 1796, 277, 2113, 369, 277, 1658, 29718, 730, 5073, 263, 11, 16742, 13, 50668], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 400, "seek": 172754, "start": 1733.92, "end": 1734.56, "text": " E a terceira?", "tokens": [50684, 462, 257, 41385, 4271, 30, 50716], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 401, "seek": 172754, "start": 1734.8, "end": 1740.54, "text": " A terceira e talvez a mais complexa \u00e9 a coer\u00eancia do caminho.", "tokens": [50728, 316, 41385, 4271, 308, 32320, 257, 2420, 3997, 64, 1136, 257, 598, 260, 9322, 360, 37215, 13, 51015], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 402, "seek": 172754, "start": 1741.08, "end": 1744.82, "text": " O modo como a gente navega de um ponto ao outro", "tokens": [51042, 422, 16664, 2617, 257, 3788, 39376, 3680, 368, 1105, 17936, 8130, 13170, 51229], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 403, "seek": 172754, "start": 1744.82, "end": 1748.2, "text": " precisa continuar fazendo sentido l\u00f3gico,", "tokens": [51229, 18861, 29980, 20741, 19850, 48475, 2789, 11, 51398], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 404, "seek": 172754, "start": 1748.68, "end": 1752.7, "text": " mesmo quando as eras e as plataformas mudam.", "tokens": [51422, 9082, 7770, 382, 1189, 296, 308, 382, 36448, 296, 8933, 335, 13, 51623], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13188779100458672, "compression_ratio": 1.4688995215311005, "no_speech_prob": 8.844550092312886e-12}, {"id": 405, "seek": 175270, "start": 1752.7, "end": 1756.3, "text": " O significado de uma ideia n\u00e3o \u00e9 est\u00e1tico.", "tokens": [50365, 422, 3350, 1573, 368, 2772, 26409, 2431, 1136, 3192, 83, 2789, 13, 50545], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667709238388958, "compression_ratio": 1.5021097046413503, "no_speech_prob": 8.053833641663566e-12}, {"id": 406, "seek": 175270, "start": 1756.54, "end": 1758.88, "text": " Ele mora na rela\u00e7\u00e3o din\u00e2mica", "tokens": [50557, 8024, 1896, 64, 1667, 28177, 3791, 24484, 2262, 50674], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667709238388958, "compression_ratio": 1.5021097046413503, "no_speech_prob": 8.053833641663566e-12}, {"id": 407, "seek": 175270, "start": 1758.88, "end": 1760.9, "text": " entre quem pesquisa no presente", "tokens": [50674, 3962, 13026, 9262, 358, 3837, 572, 28709, 50775], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667709238388958, "compression_ratio": 1.5021097046413503, "no_speech_prob": 8.053833641663566e-12}, {"id": 408, "seek": 175270, "start": 1760.9, "end": 1763.2, "text": " e o que foi escrito no passado.", "tokens": [50775, 308, 277, 631, 6901, 49451, 572, 42490, 13, 50890], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12667709238388958, "compression_ratio": 1.5021097046413503, "no_speech_prob": 8.053833641663566e-12}, {"id": 409, "seek": 175270, "start": 1763.82, "end": 1767.2, 