"no_speech_prob": 1.183150149033918e-12}, {"id": 9, "seek": 4988, "start": 60.78, "end": 65.88, "text": " We're going to uncover the hidden mechanics of how meaning actually survives over time.", "tokens": [50910, 492, 434, 516, 281, 21694, 264, 7633, 12939, 295, 577, 3620, 767, 46231, 670, 565, 13, 51165], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11930098798539904, "compression_ratio": 1.559090909090909, "no_speech_prob": 1.183150149033918e-12}, {"id": 10, "seek": 4988, "start": 66.76, "end": 71.30000000000001, "text": " And spoiler alert, it has very little to do with the size of your hard drive.", "tokens": [51209, 400, 26927, 9615, 11, 309, 575, 588, 707, 281, 360, 365, 264, 2744, 295, 428, 1152, 3332, 13, 51436], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11930098798539904, "compression_ratio": 1.559090909090909, "no_speech_prob": 1.183150149033918e-12}, {"id": 11, "seek": 7130, "start": 71.3, "end": 79.8, "text": " No, it really doesn't. And that's what makes this such a fundamental shift in how we analyze knowledge systems.", "tokens": [50365, 883, 11, 309, 534, 1177, 380, 13, 400, 300, 311, 437, 1669, 341, 1270, 257, 8088, 5513, 294, 577, 321, 12477, 3601, 3652, 13, 50790], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13834237448776823, "compression_ratio": 1.475206611570248, "no_speech_prob": 1.5674108061816683e-12}, {"id": 12, "seek": 7130, "start": 80.12, "end": 84.42, "text": " I mean, we allocate massive amounts of capital towards storage infrastructure.", "tokens": [50806, 286, 914, 11, 321, 35713, 5994, 11663, 295, 4238, 3030, 6725, 6896, 13, 51021], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13834237448776823, "compression_ratio": 1.475206611570248, "no_speech_prob": 1.5674108061816683e-12}, {"id": 13, "seek": 7130, "start": 84.78, "end": 84.89999999999999, "text": " Right.", "tokens": [51039, 1779, 13, 51045], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13834237448776823, "compression_ratio": 1.475206611570248, "no_speech_prob": 1.5674108061816683e-12}, {"id": 14, "seek": 71